title: Remente: Self Improvement
description:
This app listens. Based on your needs it provides a bunch of tools to help you elevate your life.

Live a healthy and rich life with a system of personal development tools to help you focus, be organised, productive as well as goal and action oriented. Perfect for a new year's resolution! The skill and knowledge provided will help you maintain your mental wellbeing and enable you to live a rich and healthy life with greater self esteem, more self worth and less stress and anxiety. 

The app contains the following:
A day planner that contains daily to-do’s as well as long term goal actions and tasks.
A life assessment tool that gives you an overview of your focus in life.
A mood journal that explains what affects your mood and why you feel bad.
A curated collection of articles and exercises about every aspect of life. 
A gallery of expertly crafted goal plans you can use to grow.

Mentioned in Forbes!

Goal setting guide
Becoming better and achieving personal growth and development can only be achieved by creating good goals and habits. Remente acts as your coach and offer guides and tips for setting and achieving goals that form sustainable habits which result in healthy behavior. 

The Day Planner
To reach goals and form habits you need to plan, and be reminded of, when it’s time to take action. The day planner is a smart and dynamic to-do list which plans your days for you based on your goals.

Life assessment
Tracking how your life is balancing is important for your mental wellbeing and to reduce your stress and anxiety levels. The life assessment tool helps you determine where you should focus your personal development efforts to become mindful and healthy.

Mood Journal
Learn what makes you feel good with the Remente mood journal.
By tracking your mood you will understand what consequences your behaviours and habits have on your mental wellbeing and life. You can also use tags like “stressed” or “confident” to learn more about emotions like self esteem. What habits increase your self esteem? Use the mood journal to find out.  

Insights
Integrate with Google Fit to see how your body and mind affect each other. 

Expert goal plans
We have a library full of expertly crafted goal plansto coach you. They contain detailed plans, tips and information for how to succeed with common personal development goals. 

Courses & Articles
Personal development and growth requires knowledge. We provide that knowledge in the form of courses and articles written by psychologists, business managers, life coaches and world champions in several fields. Here are some of the topics we cover:

Time Management
Productivity & efficiency
Sleep Optimization
Memory Training
Friends & Social Interactions
Better Relationships, tips on dating & sex
Diets & Good Health
Stress Management
Anxiety Relief
Mindfulness
Motivation & Goal Setting
Personal Finance tips
Good Communication
Better Leadership
Making Good Decisions
Depression

Premium
We offer a premium subscription which contains several extra features and content that will help you grow even more. 

The purchase is handled by your Google-account. You can always cancel or change your subscription directly in Google Play by going to settings after your purchase.
 
The subscription will be renewed 24 hours before it expires with a subscription identical to the one you last purchased. It is not possible to cancel an already purchased subscription.
 
Terms of use & Privacy policy
https://member.remente.com/terms-of-usage

The team behind Remente are experts in the fields of psychology, coaching and mental training. Previously, we’ve helped Sweden win the 2014 World Memory Championships, pioneered internet psychiatry treatments and coached world class athletes to achieve more and do better.

So far we have helped over 100.000 people with their mental wellbeing and reaching their goals. Allow us to help you as well and become a member of the Remente family. Thank you.

summary: Goals, Habits & Journaling for Everyday Wellbeing
developerAddress: Stora Badhusgatan 18-20, 411 21 Gothenburg, Sweden
recentChanges: Various minor bug fixes. Thank you for your feedback!
comments: I've used this app for about a year now, and I've used it almost daily. However, for the past month or so, the app crashes whenever I try opening it. I've uninstalled and reinstalled it multiple times and nothing has changed.

I absolutely love this app. The only things I would love to see added are to be able to have sub-categories and sub-steps of goals (with their own reminders, not just the checklist optiom we have currently) and to be able to schedule recurring tasks multiple times per day/month/year not just per week.

This app is great and the support team is fast and friendly and I'm having a bit of trouble finding the right course for me but I just downloaded it recently and there are thousands of courses so I'm sure I'll find something. I kind of wish they had courses for specific mental illnesses like depression anxiety and eating disorders though but that's the only really thing I can think of at the moment that I'd change.

Remente is a wonderful app! So user friendly, with great tools such as the lifewheel and mood rating. It has helped me a lot with my wellbeing and to gain clarity. I love it! And highly recommend it!!
Easy to use. I wish the reminders would work better with my phone

comments: Just starting to use the app and it works perfectly for me. Simple and easy to use. Just a comment: Can add an option to sort the diary entries? Sometimes I want to view it by the diary date, the created date, or title; depending on my use. Tried to do so just now but cannot find a way. Would be really useful if the feature is available.

Such a cool app, but the problem is that I don't want to pay to be able to use certain things. I get it, that's how you make money and whatnot but still, I just want to write the entries like I would write them on a piece of paper. With everything available. Still the app is really cool and I love it.

The app's pretty good, it has different themes, different emotes on each entry, and way, way, more. I'm not gonna complain that it isn't free (not all features are there cause I didn't pay for premium) cause I understand that companies have to find a way to make money. I really recommend this app for anyone who likes journaling or just wants to try it out!

First of all, I would like to thank you so much for the existence of this journaling app! I have tried other apps in the past and I'm glad I have finally found this one! The themes are simplistic, beautiful and calming. And I really adore the quality of the stickers, it gives such an aesthetic touch to the diary entries. May I suggest a Web version for the diary? I appreciate the Google sync feature, but a Web version would do wonders. I can't write on the computer because I can't install the app and sync. If there's a Web version, surely I'll be able to write on the computer just as I would on my phone or tablet. And I would really love if you add more free stickers, I love them so much. So far, I'm giving it 5 stars. No ads or constant pop-ups to buy the premium. It's all very relaxing and appropriate for journaling. Keep it up!

Everything about this app is AWESOME! I have to found any problems. I love how if you forgot your password you can type questions! Oh wait.. here's my actual problem.... Nothing! Also I'm so glad that there are no ads!

title: 21 Days Challenge
description:
Create your ideal life with life changing habits.
It is estimated that it takes people 21 days to form a new habit. So it’s a perfect amount of time to change or introduce something new in your life. Choose the best challenge for you and do it for 21 days and you’re going to see how the habit becomes part of your lifestyle day by day.

Starting a healthy lifestyle, taking a break away from the internet, practicing gratitude, trying to be more productive, simple practices to find happiness and calm in your life, how to study effectively for all the students, ways to spread kindness and positivity, tips for fixing your sleeping schedule and daily positive affirmations are some of the challenges that you can find in the app.

Once you complete your daily task, you can mark as completed and collect the points (to customize your avatar). This way, you can use this app like a habit tracker.

In the gratitude challenge, you can write your thoughts and share them in the feed (you can leave anonymously too). Here you're going to see all the community answers and you can also give it a like on your favorite ones.

Complete tasks on your profile and do daily challenges to collect points so you can buy items for your own avatar like different hairstyles, eyes and mouth shapes and clothes.
Create a healthier and happier mind with journaling. With this app you can daily journal and choose your daily mood. Then you can track your mood in the calendar and see all your previous records.
You also a have a selection of positive wallpapers for your phone.

Enable notifications and choose the time to be notified to remind you to do the challenge every day.

Don’t forget to take care of your body and mind. It's the only place you have to live.

recentChanges:
New challenges
UI improvements

comments: I love it 😍 soooo much. At first i thought that it only had the default challenges, and i was about to look for another app to complement it. But then i realized that you can set your own challenges and tailor them to your exact needs. That is when i jumped for joy. I have needed something like this all my life ❤️ thank you so much and God bless you. Keep up the amazing work . Also after the 21 days are over you can restart the challenge ( with the same daily steps or change them).So flexible ☺

An update. I removed 2 stars from my review for the following reasons: 1. Volume control/mute doesn't exist in settings. The ads are very jarring and come by surprise. 2. I created my own challenge, and none of the days saved. Every scratch was blank so I deleted it. Finally, a habit tracker that I actually like! I like how simple and streamlined the app is. Not hard to use. Easy to adapt the challenge to your individual needs if the suggestion for the day doesn't apply to you.

A real app that you can use in life..I love the topics, the suggestions really work and you can tell it was made with very good intentions. I do not force myself to follow what comes up day by day, but I do return to all the unchecked ones and see what chances come to complete them in the flow of the day. A good balance between being in the flow and directing your life. I love it. Thank you.

I absolutely love this app. I use it every day and it makes me so happy; especially the the tiny motivational and heartfelt quotes that you get as notifications every day, it's so wholesome to hear "it's okay to be emotional, it's what makes you human, beautiful and powerful" (for example) after a rough day ^^ i always smile when i receive those notifications and it makes me feel so much better

My favourite thing is the daily little inspirational notification which sometimes comes at the best time to pick me up if my mood is not that great. I like the diversity of the challenges, the structure of them and although it might sound silly, I do like the idea of scratching a card to find out your daily task, it boosts the excitement and puts me in a good headspace to get the task done. Great job to the developers and implementers!! Also, I do really enjoy the colour scheme, very calming

title: Handy for Pros
description:
Are you a cleaning pro, handyman, or other home service professional? Download the Handy for Pros app to showcase your skills, connect with customers looking for home services, and build your business.

It’s easy to get started on the Handy platform! Just download the app, create an account and let us know which types of home services you’re looking to provide. You can claim jobs, set your business hours, communicate with your clients, and start earning once you’ve been activated on the platform.

There are thousands of potential clients looking for home service professionals like you all over the country. Download the app and get started today!

View Handy’s Privacy Policy and CA Pre-Collection Notice at handy.com/privacy.
descriptionHTML:
Are you a cleaning pro, handyman, or other home service professional? Download the Handy for Pros app to showcase your skills, connect with customers looking for home services, and build your business.

It’s easy to get started on the Handy platform! Just download the app, create an account and let us know which types of home services you’re looking to provide. You can claim jobs, set your business hours, communicate with your clients, and start earning once you’ve been activated on the platform.

There are thousands of potential clients looking for home service professionals like you all over the country. Download the app and get started today!

View Handy’s Privacy Policy and CA Pre-Collection Notice at handy.com/privacy.
summary: Find Cleaning and Handyman Jobs.
comments: I love the concept of this app, however needs lots of work with detailed description for homes. And should charge more for extra living spaces. Some homes have more than one living space and even multiple dining rooms. Most customers will expect it to be included. But there just isn't enough time. Also time frames to get a job done is not enough then job will feel rushed. Size of home should be a requirement including sq feet. Also description should show before job acceptance.

I'm enjoying the extra income, especially since I was in between jobs. It kept food on the table. However, I really REALLY believe there should be a distance filter. Honestly, who would drive 50+ miles one-way for a furniture assembly? It seems obvious to me. I also noticed that I get notifications for jobs that I don't have selected in my filters, and they're usually pretty far away.

The two issues that I get the most are when clients need to 1. Reschedule work because they need to pick up some supplies for some work that needs to be done or they need to adjust the time frame of the work and they have a problem going to the app and doing so easil. Please update the app and make it so that the clients have some sort of tutorial that shows them how to make simple adjustments to make it easier for them to contact the handy pro that has claimed their work assignment.

The app is buggy, I've uploaded my photo 20 times with no success. They expect you to carry a thermometer on you 24/7, because you have to tell them your temperature randomly, even if your just checking your schedule. When I respond that I didn't know my temperature, I was threatened with disciplinary action! The pay for the handyman stuff is... okay, as long as it's local, the pay for house cleaning is a joke... it's not a bad side job, and a great way to meet people who might hire you again.

I am having a serious hard time with this app after installation. The company seems to be faceless as you can't reach anyone when you're stock. My application is still in review for months after completing the onboarding application process. I am taking my picture and watch the videos and it's just there for months. The annoying part is my the $20 which I paid so as to get started and there's no phone number or email for you to contact anyone.

title: Daylio - Diary, Journal, Mood Tracker
description:
Daylio enables you to keep a private journal without having to type a single line. Try this beautifully designed & stunningly simple micro-diary app right now for FREE!


😁 WHAT IS DAYLIO

Daylio is a very versatile app, and you can turn it in whatever you need to track. Your fitness goal pal. Your mental health coach. Your food log. Your gratitude diary. Mood tracker. Exercise, meditate, eat, and be grateful. Take care of your mental, emotional, and physical health. Good self-care is a key to improved mood and reduced anxiety.

This is the time for your wellbeing, self-improvement, and self-care. Use Daylio as your daily bullet journal. We build it on three principles:

✅ Reach happiness and self-improvement by being mindful of your days.
✅ Validate your hunches. How does your new hobby influence your life?
✅ Form a new habit in an obstacle-free environment—no learning curve. Daylio is super simple to use, create your first entry in two steps.

For anxiety and stress relief, make sure to include activities that help you to cope with negativity. Everybody can use a mood boost! You can measure their impact on your mood in stats. 


🤔 HOW DOES IT WORK

Pick your mood and add activities you have been doing during the day. You can also add notes and keep an old school diary. Daylio is collecting recorded moods and activities in the statistics and calendar. This format will help you to understand your habits better. Keep track of your activities and create patterns to become more productive!

You can review all entries in the statistics on charts or the calendar and share them with your friends.

To make it even better, Daylio allows you:
⭐ Make reflection a daily habit
⭐ Discover what makes you happy
⭐ Use a big database of beautiful icons for your personalized activities 
⭐ Mix and match your own moods using funny emojis
⭐ Explore exciting statistics about your life on weekly, monthly or yearly charts
⭐ Deep dive into advanced statistics for every mood, activity or group
⭐ Customize color themes
⭐ Enjoy nights with dark mode
⭐ See your whole year in 'Year in Pixels'
⭐ Create daily, weekly or monthly goals and motivate yourself
⭐ Build habits and collect achievements
⭐ Share statistics with your friends
⭐ Safely back up and restore your entries via your private Google Drive
⭐ Set reminders and never forget to create a memory
⭐ Turn on PIN lock and keep your diary safe
⭐ Export PDF and CSV documents to share or print your entries


🧐 PRIVACY AND SECURITY

We are a top private journal since we do not store or collect your data.

At Daylio, we believe in transparency and honesty. Your data is stored locally on your phone. You can optionally schedule backups to your private cloud storage or take your backup file with you anywhere. Data are entirely under your control at all times.

Data stored in the app's private directories are not accessible by any other apps or processes. Your backups are transferred to the Google Drive via the secure (encrypted) channels.

We don't send your data to our servers. We don't have access to your entries. Also, any other third-party app can't read your data.

⭐ See your whole year in 'Year in Pixels'
⭐ Create daily, weekly or monthly goals and motivate yourself
⭐ Build habits and collect achievements
⭐ Share statistics with your friends
⭐ Safely back up and restore your entries via your private Google Drive
⭐ Set reminders and never forget to create a memory
⭐ Turn on PIN lock and keep your diary safe
⭐ Export PDF and CSV documents to share or print your entries


🧐 PRIVACY AND SECURITY

We are a top private journal since we do not store or collect your data.

At Daylio, we believe in transparency and honesty. Your data is stored locally on your phone. You can optionally schedule backups to your private cloud storage or take your backup file with you anywhere. Data are entirely under your control at all times.

Data stored in the app's private directories are not accessible by any other apps or processes. Your backups are transferred to the Google Drive via the secure (encrypted) channels.

We don't send your data to our servers. We don't have access to your entries. Also, any other third-party app can't read your data.

recentChanges: Thanks for using Daylio. We have made several small improvements and fixed a couple of bugs. Enjoy the app!
comments: Far more useful and life-improving than expected! I've been using daylio every single day for almost 2 years, which is both an achievement and a testament to the app's ease-of-use. It's still being actively developed so great new features keep popping up. An app that I'm very happy to support and recommend.

I bought the app, but when I switched my phone, they didn't saved my purchase, restricting me in use of the app. Although premium version still valid and working on the old phone. Ridiculous! Btw: asking monthly subscription for the app, for which you don't even need to pay for servers, is the most violent insult of your users🖕

Great tool to help you keep track of life. I like the fact it works with speech to text so I don't actually have to type down my journal throughout the day and it helps keep track of things I want to do things I'd like to do and just things like that. it reminds me to do stuff a lot which honestly sometimes I would forget and it's honestly help me a lot with my depression by just reminding me to like be kind to myself and things like that. I highly recommend it.

I have struggles with remembering to do simple daily tasks and keeping a routine in place. This is the only app I pay for because its the easiest to use and the only one that's ever actually managed to keep me on task and keep track of things. I highly recommend it for anyone with executive dysfunction, ADHD or autism if you need help staying on task or remembering daily self care!!

Great mood and activity tracker. I would really like the ability to still log things after midnight as the same day. I am having to customise the time and date for late night entries because they don't make sense to include in the next day. I haven't started that day yet! I think a "day start/end time" we can set would be an easy fix, much like choosing if weeks start on Sunday or Monday. I hope you consider this feedback!

comments: I can't speak to other peoples experiences, but I'm a young guy 22 and I turned this app on because I live in a place where there aren't a lot of twenty something year olds. I've gotten 3 phone numbers in like 4 days of using the app, went on a few days and actually like both of the girls. So for me the app really works! I think these dating apps are what you make of it and some people who don't get swiped right might get salty and leave a bad review, believe me it is very possible to get dates and enjoy fetlife!

Paid subscriber. This seems super sketch. Not saying all their profiles are fake but the lions share appear to be. The people i talk to are a portion of the same ones from a different kink app I subscribe to. No one else has responded, or matched, and you get a sense that the profiles, and the photos don't really sync. Id rather see less people on that are real, rather than sift through lies.

Unable to message, unless you pay. I bit the bullet, and got a 1 month subscription. But, since very few pay. It's impossible to communicate. Because, the person you're interested in, can't reply. What is the point of subscribing and supporting the app; when you get nothing for it? Pretty sure, most of the people in my geographical location (Pittsburgh) haven't used the app in over a month. What's the point of using an app, that most people cant use and give up on?

No ads, most of the profiles seem real, and the subscription is not prohibitively expensive. The free use is ok, but it would be cool to be able to send one message a week or something to initiate contact. I would really like to see a way to search within a certain distance, and a way to apply the same filter for the swipe game. Unfortunately, there are a lot of females ' selling services ' or foot pics.The community seems to be on the small side. Overall, it's not bad, but it's not great.

It's ok, same as all the others when it comes to being able to use very basic features until you pay. My issue is that I cannot scroll up through messages I receive. So if someone sends me a few messages in a row, I cannot go up to read them. It's incredibly dumb. Not to mention you cannot avoid being contacted by people way outside your preferred age range. I've had to block more people than I have spoken to. And they don't have to use a picture of their face to start a profile.

title: Lifestyle AI - Nutritionist & Healthy Meal Planner
description:
Lifestyle AI is a personal nutritionist that delivers perfectly tailored meal plans and food options to you. We use machine-learning algorithms to learn about your personal profile & tastes so that our food recommendations will always bring you one step closer to your fitness and nutrition goals. Our foods include a mix of takeaways, ready-to-eat/cook meals, and recipes.

Here of some of the top features:

Convenient Meal Recommendations
Lifestyle AI will deliver convenient food recommendations for each meal, dynamically adjusted to suit your profile. For every meal, we'll give you several options to choose from which are always tailored precisely to you and the progress you’re making towards your goals. Our food recommendation gives you recipes along with takeaways and ready meals you can get from retailers in your area. Or if you'd prefer, you can enter your own meals and they'll be recommended back to you when they suit you best. Forget having to rely only on time-consuming recipes to live a healthy lifestyle, we can integrate into even the busiest of schedules!

Powered by Machine Learning
Our set of advanced algorithms will constantly be adjusting to bring you as close as possible to your goal. We'll also learn what you like along the way, so the process isn't an unsustainable diet but rather a lifestyle tweak with amazing results. Simply tell us your goal (e.g. lose 10 pounds by summer), and we'll handle the rest. All your nutrition will be planned out by the algorithm - every meal we give you will bring you one step closer!

Calorie counter, food tracking, fitness tracking & more
Lifestyle AI is also completely featured with everything you need in a calorie counter and fitness app. Manually add foods from our extensive database, create your own and track several macros and nutrients - all for free! We can also track your exercise habits, weight, and body fat, and then use this information to adjust your meal recommendations so that you're always getting the perfect fit.

Other Features Include:
- Meal recommendations with up to 15 different options per meal
- Automatic machine-learning driven nutritional management - our algorithm will determine your precise needs, with daily updates
- Food tracking with an extensive food database
- Food verification - no more inaccurate food entries!
- Free tracking of all macronutrients
- Import data from other fitness apps
- Alcohol tracking - track alcohol accurately as a separate macronutrient
- Track your exercise and search our extensive exercise database
- Track your weight and body fat over time

Tracking alchohol is super unique and useful as it is hard to track in other apps.
Awesome app.With this app we get to know our health and nutrition requirment.

5/5 a really great app. Other similar apps pale in comparison. The amount of personal customization is excellent and allows for good accuracy and actually achieving goals. All the food data is verified and accurate (a big problem on other apps)! As someone who struggles with designing meals the recommender is really useful. The calorie breakdown is a great feature. This app has a beautiful smooth design and includes many useful graphs and diagrams.
Too limited
FABULOUS APP

title: Natural Remedies: healthy life, food and beauty
description:
Love nature and find in nature your wellness. The health app for your healthy life, with healthy recipes, healthy food, herbal teas, health tips for natural beauty and skincare. But it does not end here, in fact you can also read lot of recipes of natural cosmetics and the latest news from science about nutrition and healthy natural life.

Toothache, insomnia, acne as well as nausea are just some of the illnesses that can be treated with natural methods without the overuse of medicines. Nature can be really a useful help.

Natural remedies such as herbal tea, essential oils, mother tinctures, antiwrinkle natural cosmetics and glycerin macerate act slowly, require patience but they can be very helpful and do not have the collateral effects related to medicines.

This health app, easy and fast, is a handbook of the natural remedies for the most common diseases, a book of healthy recipes, a place where you can find tips for a healthy life, for your skincare, to get healthy and stay healthy

The app for your natural wellness is structured as follows:

NATURAL REMEDIES
A list of plants, fruits and essential oils with explanations about uses, properties and benefits.

PROBLEMS AND DISEASES
List of the most common illnesses (allergy, poor digestion, acne, joint pain,  nausea, anxiety, wrinkles and much more) with the related natural remedies.

HEALTHY RECIPES & HEALTHY DIET & HEALTHY FOOD
Every week one healthy recipe to keep you fit and healthy with taste. Enjoy the yummy healthy food.

YOGA EXERSICES
For the flexibility of the body and the calm of mind. Yoga for the back, for the sciatica, to detox the body, for beginners and advanced.

HEALTHY NEWS FROM SCIENCE
Last news from science world: the most recent scientific studies about lifestyle, wellness, nutrition and health are reported.

SMALL NATURAL TIPS & TRICKS
Small and health tips and tricks for every day: short video tutorials that show you how to prepare at home simple natural remedies and natural cosmetics for your skincare and beauty, antiwrinkle lotions, lip gloss for cracked lips, golden milk, remedy for swollen legs.

CRHOMOTHERAPY
This section is based on the color-method to induce relax before bed. 

RELAX AREA
Enjoy the nature with sounds and calming music to relax your mind and body. 


Some topics that you can find on the app Natural Remedies are: information and application about Aloe Vera, how to prepare the Golden Milk, but also the green tee Matcha. You can read also the properties of turmeric, find out the essential oils that you can use against anxiety or depression. Do you have friends for lunch? Maybe you can find interesting the cake without butter or the healthy recipes for every day. In addition to this, you can also learn how to prepare DIY beauty cosmetics also in case of acne or wrinkles. Finally you can learn about eye health tips, healthy eating tips or healthy hair tips



Disclaimer
This app is not a substitute for professional medical or health advice, examination, diagnosis, or treatment. This app disclaims any liability for the decisions you make based on this information.

comments: The music, relaxation and meditation portion with the various styles of sound and music choices is phenomenal. I have anxiety issues and I didn't have any idea how much it would help. I love this option of the app but there's so much more. The health, healthy diet alternatives, natural remedies, wow, life changing info in this app! And it was like every day there was something new to find out. Love it!!
Very informative. Especially since the pandemic and the medication(s) abuse going on in our society. Being able to find natural remedies is a godsend. I also have found a medicinal plant app too.
I love how you can type in a sickness or cold or sore leg muscles & it will bring up a bunch of different remedies to try. A very easy & clear app love it 💕

This is an amazing app. It literally tells u all kinds of home made natural remedies and recipes u can use or make to use. For me, I've been having trouble with acne and it gave me a huge list with good detailing on what I need, and how to use it, and how to make it. It's not just for acne though. Upset stomach, in general just wanting to b healthy. It's a great app. At least for me it is. It's worth it to check out if ur into stuff like this

The site is amazing from A to Z and then some. It goes far beyond my expectations, especially considering it's free! It's a plethora of information ! Not to mention the advertisements are minimal and not intrusive ! 100% recommend this app

title: Deepstash - Self Improvement, Motivation & Care
description:
Think of Deepstash as your personal library of thoughts and knowledge. A daily source of inspiring & life changing stories and ideas. Read articles, learn skills, get productivity tips and discover life hacks. All curated by our team and presented to you in a simple, practical and easy to remember, short summarized format. Fuel your curiosity and get smarter daily.

It's like your social media feed, if your social media feed had things that mattered :-)

Content & articles that matter to you. Our team curates the best stories around the web (articles, videos, podcasts & more, from top publications and magazines like Medium, Inc, Lifehacker, Forbes, Mark Manson, FastCompany, BBC, Tony Robbins & more) and provides actionable and inspiring short form key insights to improve yourself personally and professionally. A wealth of self help knowledge in your pocket.

Have questions? You’ll surely get answers by reading, learning and exploring a world of hard and soft skills as well as interests like time management, self improvement, leadership, self-confidence, motivation or psychology, that will make you a great fit anywhere in life you put your mind to.

Summarized ideas. You need just 5 minutes per day. Our team works for you. We provide a summary of the main insights of articles and other web content in a short and crisp 100 words or less format we call “ideas”.

Escape the negativity and time wasting pull of social media platforms. Our app’s goal is to help you towards self improvement and self care and to get you motivated, inspired, wiser and productive.

Personalized content & feed. Choose a few topics of interest (like self improvement, time management, problem solving, love & relationships & more) and then just use the app at your leisure. As you save ideas and use our app, we learn what you like and find the best stories and articles to show you every day, so you’re motivated and inspired. You don’t even have to work for it.

The more you save ideas the better we learn what articles and topics you love. We refresh your recommendations multiple times a day so you never run out of fresh stories and ideas.

Build and organize your knowledge. You can save ideas in your own personal profile and build your own hub of facts, skills, quotes, information and ideas that matter to you.

Search and filter your ideas and articles by recent, oldest or most popular and organise your knowledge into personalised stashes, which are basically collections of insights stocked up and ready to go for when you need them: a Powerpoint presentation, a new job interview, a date, a project at work, or negotiating your rent with the landlord.

Share your knowledge. We make it super easy for you to share the best articles, quotes, stories and ideas on any channel you want. Send it to a friend on Whatsapp or share it with your followers on Instagram.

Share a link to ideas or just an image. We built special image formats for each social network (Instagram, Facebook, Twitter and others) so your ideas look best.

No ads. No distractions. 100% Free. The Deepstash app is free and open to everyone. Get a clean reading experience and focus on the content instead of being distracted with annoying ads or dozens of notifications about “premium” subscriptions. Just get a quick free account (Facebook & Google login) and you’re good to go. 

And we’ll never sell, lease or share your data. Your privacy is really important to us.

Learn new things and become a better, smarter you, with the Deepstash app!

We're always open to feedback, ideas and thoughts about anything that might make our app the best app it can be. Give us a shout at hello@deepstash.com. We read every single email we get :-)

Have a look at our website and social stuff:

deepstash.com
instagram.com/deepstash
twitter.com/deepstash
facebook.com/deepstash

We (sometimes) write on Medium: https://medium.com/infinite-learners

title: Type 2 Diabetes: Lifestyle & BG by Nourishly
description:
If you have Type 2 Diabetes or Pre-Diabetes this app will help you make lifestyle changes that you know you need to do but find it hard to do.

Built with input from leading dietitians, psychologists and researchers, this free and HIPAA compliant app puts "what works" for diabetes management in your pocket:

☆  Easily log blood glucose, meals, medication, physical activity, and stress
☆  Learn how these things affect your blood sugar levels
☆  Link with your care team for data sharing and feedback
☆  Discover easy (and tasty) diabetes meal plans
☆  Over 100 science backed micro-missions to master!

6 Reasons why you should give it a try:

1. Link with your care team: Turbo charge the care you receive by linking with your Dietitian, Nutritionist, Psychologist, Doctor, Social Worker, Health Coach or Nurse Practitioner for insight-driven care and feedback both in AND out of the clinic. 

2. Personalized meal, blood glucose, activity and symptom trackers: You are multi-dimensional, and so should be your trusted tracker! Break free from stock-standard glucose monitoring with integrated symptom, mood, meal and activity tracking. 

3. Stress free and flexible meal planning: Pick from expert curated weekly diabetes meal plans, create your own, or link with your nutrition expert for a plan personalized for you. 

4. 100 Science-backed missions to choose from: Gradually master proven habit-hacks for diabetes that can help avoid blood sugar spikes and dips, and regulate your body weight.

5. Celebrate wins with rewards: Be surprised and delighted by beautiful, funny and thought provoking reflection images and affirmations.

6. Coping skills for when you get stuck: Take advantage of 200+ skills to unstick yourself when mental blockers, negative-self talk, lethargy and anxiety strike.

title: Habinator - Health & Life Coach to Create Habits
description:
Habinator™ is a Health Advisor and Life-Coach which helps you reach goals in areas like health, work, relationships, and self-improvement. You can also track daily habits and routines.

Create a scientifically based individual plan tailored for your desired lifestyle changes. Habinator guides, educates, reminds, and supports you on your way to success. It's your companion for positive change. You will grow to be a master of yourself and become the person you want to be! Join the worldwide community of achievers.

Free to use. No ads.
Based on the latest scientific data.

THE APP IS FOR YOU IF YOU WANT TO
★ Make a change in your life
★ Build new habits, daily routines or quit bad habits
★ You want to get more energy, happiness or better mood
★ You need a clear process and coaching how to change
★ You have a dream but don't know how to get started

Looking for a habit tracker? Habinator is like a habit tracker, but better. If you want to change habits or quit bad habits, simply deciding to is usually not enough. Habinator gives you predefined reasons and scientifically proven strategies to make the change happen. It motivates you by asking questions and giving feedback about your progress enabling you to find your intrinsic motivation. Tapping into the inner motivations and achieving self-actualization and self-improvement is not an easy task, but Habinator is the best tool available to get there.

Hundreds of editable goals are grouped into searchable domains and categories, like
★ Health - Diet & Nutrition, Longevity, Mental Health, Sleep & Recovery, Exercise
★ Self-improvement - Creativity, Energy, Mindset, Morning Routines,  
★ Work - Time Management, Self-Esteem, Communication, Productivity
★ Relationships - Family, Friends, Intimacy, Parenting
★ Addictions - Alcohol, Smoking, Technology, Stress Reduction
★ Finance - Learning, Business, Money, Education, Study
★ Spirituality - Presence & Attendance, Religion, Tolerance

HOW DOES IT WORK?
1. Create a goal.
2. Define your motivation, reasons for change, outcomes, and an emergency plan.
3. Habinator guides, track, and motivates your progress.
4. Just keep going along with your plan and the success will be inevitable!

Create your own lifestyle medicine program and begin to reach your goals in life. Now.

FEATURES
★ Set personalized goals from predefined templates which include research references for motivation and to help you learn more about your goal
★ Create your own emergency plan
★ Ask for help from the community to support
★ Get custom reminders to help you follow your daily schedule
★ Track your progress
★ Benefit from exercises for motivation, self-perception, and to overcome addictions

The app is based on science in areas like self-actualization, goal achievement, and positive psychology. Predefined goals give you references to articles in the research fields like medicine, productivity, nutrition, behavioral neuroscience.

Learn more about our research: https://habinator.com/research-resources


Habinator™ is the leading behavior change platform for individuals and professionals.

title: Personality Development: Lifestyle, Tips & Hacks
description:
Now is the time to stay home calm and improve your inner health and stay focused and motivational. We offer a variety of music, meditate, relax and sleep better motivational quotes so you can read them at home and stay calm and relaxed. Our meditation and the relaxing app is the perfect mindfulness app for everyone and can help grow your emotional well-being through deep meditation and sleep relaxation.

Personality development is the development of the calm and organized pattern of behaviors and attitudes that makes a person distinctive. Personality development occurs through the ongoing interaction of temperament, character, and environment. Life can be stressful and many people in their life experience depression, anxiety, sleep deprivation, stress, and restlessness. 

Though everyone is born unique, we all possess certain traits that set us apart from the rest. These traits define who we are and how we respond to situations. Often, we end up clinging onto the ones that do more harm than good and end up undervaluing ourselves. The fact, however, remains that we are all unique in our own ways and only need to ignite that dormant passion and give a boost to our persona. This is where personality development comes in and stays calm and focused.

Personality Development: Lifestyle, Tips & Hacks is a trendy and professional app that mainly focused on developing the organized behavior of an individual through tons of real-life expert advice and helpful tips. The app also provides daily motivational and inspirational quotes to keep you motivated and stay focused. This app will also help you in improving your lifestyle with easy to follow articles and suggestions.

Personality Development Tips:

1.	Be as positive as a proton
A proton can never lose its positivity as so can’t you! It just gets covered by stress which saps your energy. Staying positive will help you overcome the toughest of challenges while attracting more positivity and opportunities.
2.	Be more passionate
The best way to get any work done is by being passionate about it. Let your passion drive your efforts and you’ll be able to achieve excellence in life.
3.	Handle your emotions…with care
If life is a roller-coaster ride, then make sure you are enjoying it to the max. Don’t let your emotions take control of situations but learn to get a grip on them. This will help you stay centered and calm during challenging situations.
4.	Share a little, care a little
Learn to be more compassionate! The next time you or somebody else commits an error, let them off the hook without holding a grudge. Broaden your perspective that we all are evolving continuously and that no one’s perfect. This outlook will help you accept yourself and others better.
5.	Praise the one in front of you
When we praise someone’s qualities out of the feeling of completeness, then it elevates our consciousness and brings enthusiasm and energy. It helps the same qualities blossom in us too and we become better individuals.
6.	Communicate effectively
We communicate either through our presence or by expressing our feelings. Bring clarity in your communication and you’ll see people respond to you better, and more than often favorably.
7.	Be a lion in the face of danger
In the face of adversity, standing up to the challenge will make your chances of survival higher. Don’t give in to pressure and face every challenge confidently. Either you will overcome the adversity or learn something invaluable.
8.	Possess the quality of patience
Patience is the secret ingredient for becoming a winner. Feverishness and prompt reactions will do more harm than good. Remember to stay

title: Productive Lifestyle
description:
In today's ever changing society there is one thing we all have in common. That is, we have gotten busier. The constant hustle and bustle and endless to-do list is always in the back of our mind. 

It is not just about accomplishing more in less time, but being effective with your time and using it to accomplish meaningful tasks. Many people busy themselves with menial tasks but nothing substantial ever seems to get accomplished. While other can never find the time to get to the really important tasks in their day. This is where the most important lesson to be learned is. Prioritizing. Our Productive Lifestyle App will help you to prioritize your tasks more efficiently and give you tips and tricks on how to stay on track. 

Our Productive Lifestyle will help you to figure out what are your priorities, how to stop procrastinating, tips on how to stay focused and how to accomplish more in less time.

comments: Great app with easy-to-use interface. The icon happens to display my birthdate so it kinda won me over a little. Tried using it and another app for a few days and am glad it's so simple yet customisable. I also like that I can attach photos/videos in the diary. It's really like a diary on-the-go. Eventually uninstalled the other app and stuck with this. However, fingerprint unlocking is a little slow to react. Would be good if it can detect and unlock faster.

I've been using this app for more than a year. It's the most treasured diary app I have. I'm on premium and its the best. Thank you for the export to pdf function, its ingenious! And also all the back up and restore options. I was told that to log into my Google account I had to reinstall the app. It was nerve wrecking thinking about the chances of losing my data but everything worked fine. :)

Purchased the one-off premium feature, I got 50% and another RM2 discount. So far, I like the features. You can change the fonts, add pictures and emoji as emotions of your daily day. You can even take a look at others story, but you can choose to mute this feature. I wanted to write to express my emotions and I find out that this apps is compatible with my style, it's simple but all you need is there. Gonna use this for a very long time so I hope it'll always be this great! Thanks!

This app is really great!! ❤️ I Love it so much since the day i downloaded it to be honest. Its features are really cool. We could attach pictures, videos, gifs and audios etc.. And it has a mood tracks of our days and we could write our thoughts sooo much and has a lot of space to write. It even has a calendar to mark or anniversaries and can be added to all years.!!!I really love this app. Its more effective than writing a journal. 5 Stars.

I haven't had this app for long but this is great. I love the fonts and colors we can use. I also love how you can put it on private or share it with other people. Its amazing and even though not much people see it,I love it because its a diary for me but on the phone. Daily Life, your app is VERY GOOD

title: Clickastro : Horoscope & Astrology
description:
Clickastro is the leading Astrology service provider in India since 1984 and with more than 110 million customers. This app gives you FREE daily predictions, muhurtas, lucky direction, color, mantras, etc. The predictions are based on Vedic and Western astrology which you can choose based on your belief/interest. You will also have exclusive app user access to our premium horoscope reports like Career, Education, Marriage, Wealth, etc.

Highlights

- Sookshma Prana Dasa daily horoscope
- Sun sign (Zodiac sign) based daily horoscope.
- Moonsign based daily predictions (Aaj ka rashifal)
- Numerology based daily guidelines
- Daily Muhurta's
- Panchanga details daily including Rahu kal & Gulika kal
- Horoscope Matching & Love match 
- Your Horoscope summary – Yoga's & Favourable periods
- Your Detailed Horoscope with Predictions
- Consultancy with renowned astrologers in India in your language.
- Premium Horoscope reports based on Marriage, Career, Business, Transits etc. 
- Interesting good reads on astrology blog to know about latest updates.

Personalized predictions will help you make the right choices/decisions in daily life, thus making each day a successful & favorable one. This is an all-in-one astrology tool offers

- Your In-depth Horoscope (Full Horoscope)
- Premium horoscope reports on Education, Wealth, Marriage, Career, etc
- Astrology Consultancy & more

Unique features of Clickastro app

Sookshma-Prana Predictions: This unique feature can tell you what would happen in this hour and next. It’s your daily horoscope based on ongoing sookshma- prana dasas with starting & ending timings. 

Sun Sign Predictions based on Western Astrology: This helps you plan your activities knowing your zodiac sign based daily forecast.

Moon Sign Predictions or Aaj ka Rashifal: Check Moonsign or Aaj ka Rashifal predictions and decide your activities!. According to Vedic astrology moon sign decides your emotions, characteristics & mind. 

Numerology: Your daily numerology predictions with guidelines including lucky number, colour, direction etc.

Mantra of the day:  The mantra to please the deity of the day.

Muhurtas: The auspicious timings of the day for starting an activity, financial dealings, applying for a job, etc.

Daily Panchanga: Valuable astrological data including nakshatra, thithi, rahu & gulika kal and abhijith murtham.

Horoscope Summary: The favourable periods for major events in your life and your Yogas (comforts you enjoy in life).

Love Match: Do you love someone? Then check your love match – your love compatibility based on the zodiac signs.

Horoscope Matching: Kundli Matching or Thirumana Porutham is the most important step in fixing your marriage. Check it by entering the birth details of you and your prospective match.

In-depth Horoscope: Generate your Vedic Astrology based detailed Jathagam / Kundli on mobile and check it from anywhere, any time. The app prepares you detailed horoscope with predictions on all aspects and all phases of your life.

Premium Horoscope Reports: Get reports providing in-depth analyses of specific aspects of your life. These include Yearly Horoscope, Wealth Horoscope, Career & Business Horoscope, Marriage Horoscope, Transit Reports etc.

Astrology Consultancy: This app lets you consult renowned astrologers in India to get specific astrology advice/solution to your queries.

Astrology Blog: Our blog gives you more astrology insight and keeps you updated with the latest trends & developments in astrology.


This Clickastro app is currently available in English, other languages will be added soon. Do you want to check Aaj Ka Rashifal and your detailed Kundli in Hindi? Or are you looking for Today Rasi Palan and detailed Jathagam in Tamil? Let us know. 

Let the daily horoscope predictions help you plan for a better day, every day!

title: Ayurvedic Lifestyle, Diet and Home Remedies
description:
When diet is wrong, medicine is of no use; when the diet is correct, medicine is of no need.

Ayurveda believes that health is a unique balance between mind, body, and soul. Healthy diet and lifestyle habits help to maintain this balance. Ayurvigyanam app is an attempt to bring the knowledge of Ayurveda to the masses and help them to enrich their lives with ways of Ayurvedic Living.

Key features

Body Type
According to Ayurveda, the body is a composition of five-element space🌌, air💨, fire🔥, water💦, and earth🌎. These five elements combine to form three dosha (energies) of the body, namely - Vata, Pitta, and Kapha. The dominance of specific dosha inside the body denotes your Prakriti (body type). Ayurvigyanam app provides a quiz through which you can know about your body type - a.k.a. Prakriti.

Lifestyle
Ayurveda is a holistic science that outlines a healthy diet and lifestyle to harmonize with nature. The wisdom of Ayurvedic lifestyle is the high-powered approach towards healthy well-being. Ayurvedic lifestyle is a no-complicated way to spend your day with regimes like – waking up, sleeping, working, eating, and drinking. Old sages have explained day regimens (dinacharya), night regimens (ratricharya), and seasonal regimens (ritucharya) to sustain a healthy life. Following Ayurvedic regimens helps to keep your circadian rhythm in harmony. Ayurvigyanam app gives you the knowledge about these regimens and encourages you to follow them by setting reminders in the Habit section.

Diet
Ayurveda beautifully explains that each food substance has a different emphasis on the body. Each food substance has a specific action on the body, depending upon their properties. Ayurveda provides simple yet dynamic rules about diet and lifestyle. The specialty of the Ayurvedic diet is that it focuses on eating according to body type. Ayurvedic diet and lifestyle help to prevent various health problems. This app offers you an appropriate choice of diet and lifestyle habits for healthy living. There is a section of healthy recipes and a list of favorable and unfavorable food items for you according to your body type. 

Home Remedies
Ayurvedic home remedies help to maintain health and heal some minor health-related problems.  Observe your imbalances and heal the symptoms with simple home remedies before they get aggravated. Home remedies are to familiarize you with the natural methods for the self-healing of mind and body. Home remedies may reduce some symptoms, but they can not cure any disease of its root. Every disease needs proper diagnosis and treatment, which require consultation with the doctor. 

Habits
Rolling out sudden improvements in your lifestyle and diet isn't that simple. For that reason, the Ayurvigyanam application has a habit segment where you can set a reminder. Here you will discover numerous health reminders like a wake-up alarm, drinking water, meditation, yoga, and many more. You can set the health reminders as per your needs. 

Consultation
If you want to know more about Ayurvedic diet and lifestyle, you can consult our Ayurvedic doctor through the app. Your first query would be answered free of cost.

For any type of feedback or query, you can contact us at ayurvigyanam@gmail.com
If you think this application is worth sharing, then kindly do the favor and rate us to serve you better with more updates.

We hope this app will bring functional changes in your life and take you towards a natural way of healthy living. Begin your incredible adventure towards a healthy life with us.

title: KeyWe Pro
description:
Control your door lock from your Smartphone.
Don't need keys, passwords, cards. Just get the KeyWe app on your smartphone.
With the KeyWe smart system, you are always in control of your door.

Important: This App supports KeyWe original locks only. If it is not a KeyWe original Lock with KeyWe logo, the new app will not support it.

Features
 
🔑 Easy Invitation
Use the app to easily invite your family, friends, and guests. You can set up a date and time as you wish. No need to share your pin code anymore.
 
✉️ One Tap Invite
You got a delivery coming but you can’t be at home? Just send a Pin Code valid for only 5 minutes from the One Tap Invite.
 
🖖 Airbnb invite
When you have the KeyWe lock and app, it’s super easy to invite your guest on Airbnb. Not only is it easy to invite, but very useful to manage your guest. It will be a must-have tool!  
 
🚨 Real-time push notifications
KeyWe informs you in real-time. Get push notifications when your family gets home. (Some Lock types offer more features than others. Check www.thekeywe.com for more details)
 
✅ Entry/Access record checks
The safety of your home starts at your door. You can check the record of who has entered the house and when for the past two months.
 
🧠 Smart KeyWe
The door lock unlocks automatically when you approach the door lock with your smartphone based on the location tracking system.
Feel unsafe with your door opening automatically? Try the 'Magic Touch' option. When you touch your door lock with your hand, it unlocks. 
 
🚪 Multiple doors with one app
My house, my parents’ home, and the office - simply control multiple door locks with one app. The KeyWe app.
 
🏘 Multiple properties
Now, the KeyWe app can manage multiple properties. How many properties do you have? No Problem. Keywe’s got you. 
 
✍️ Easy registration
Experience the smart world with an easy registration. With no complicated process needed.
 


Please visit the KeyWe homepage and KeyWe online shop. You will see more features and news about the KeyWe smart system.

title: Mind - Expand Your Consciousness
description:
Learn the life-changing skills in just a few minutes a day with the Mind. Find lessons and tools on astral projection, lucid dreaming, remote viewing, dreams, meditation, subconscious and more. Download Mind to expand your consciousness and explore your spiritual and psychic self beyond your wildest imagination!

LEARN
Learn about many different topics about the body, spirit and the Mind, with the help of our 5-minute lessons.

PRACTICE
We have a set of tools that will help you practice and improve your psychic and spiritual skills - from intuition to lucid dream and so much more!

EXPERIENCE
Keep a detailed track of all your dreams, lucid dreams, psychic visions, spiritual experiences, astral projection and more with the help of our journal and see how you improve over time.

TOOLS
* Create Your OBE Technique
* Meditation Tracker
* Habit Assistant
* Lucid Dream Reminders & Reality Checks
* ESP Trainer
* Shamanic Journey
* Daily Practice Targets
* Ideogram Drill
* Vocabulary Trainer

TRACK YOUR PROGRESS
* Daily Journal
* Detailed Stats

TOPICS
* Meditation - learn to calm your mind and body while having lucidity, a must-learn for all spiritual and psychic exploration
* Dreams - a reality created by our subconscious mind, without lucidity
* Lucid Dream - a dream in which you become aware you are dreaming
* Out-of-Body Experience - OBE, astral projection, astral travel - separating spirit from the body, while maintaining lucidity
* Extrasensory Perception - ESP, intuition, being psychic

* Shamanic Journey - ancient spiritual practice of traveling to the spirit (or astral) world
* Psychic Healing - heal yourself and others using the mind alone
* Afterlife - what happens with our spirit at the end?
* Spirituality - non-material spirit is part of who you are
* Religion - all religions are built on the spiritual knowledge and astral projection (OBE) of their leaders

Mind is free to download and use. There are no ads. Part of the features are free forever.

Some content is only available through an optional paid subscription.

title: AWorld in support of ActNow
description:
AWorld is the App for living sustainably in the modern world. 

Created in support of ActNow - the United Nations campaign for individual action on climate change and sustainability.

Everyone has a role in the fight against climate change.
Join other people just like you

Let AWorld guide and inspire you in taking tangible, everyday actions towards living a sustainable lifestyle... completely FREE!

By changing your habits and making choices that have a less harmful impact on the environment, you have the power to confront the climate challenge and build a more sustainable world.
Here, you’ll find interactive and inspiring content to help you on your journey. You'll find tips, and challenges all geared towards making better choices part of your everyday life.

Come and learn about sustainability with our fun and gamified experience


In detail, AWorld offers:


- Journeys: Educational & inspiring content sorted in episodes to introduce you to sustainability, Sustainable Development Goals and stories about people committed in helping our planet 

- Habits: Fun and sustainable actions you can take everyday. The App will act as a reminder and give you points for taking action. 
For each action taken, the impact tracker will measure if it is water, CO2, energy or waste you are saving.


- Challenges: Groups of people that take matters into their own hands, and act for the planet. You can contribute to a challenge by taking and logging your actions. Challenges can also be sponsored by partners that pledge to make a sustainable donation if the community reaches the goal.


- Tips: Easy daily minute reads to help live a sustainable lifestyle.They come in a form of Weekly Trending topics that connect you to with what’s going on around the world		
			 
- Impact Tracker: This keeps track of your actions and shows you exactly how much your new lifestyle is saving
				
The points within AWorld measure progress towards living a sustainable lifestyle. 
You can utilize points as markers of your own sustainability journey and accumulate points to uplevel to the next stage. In moving through levels by collecting points, you can see how your own habits and actions make an impact on our planet
	
By using this App, you’ll find a pathway to action, small steps that make a big difference, and inspiration for a new kind of power. 
 
Join us and take action. Together with companies, organizations, and each other.
Because together is where real change happens. 

You can track your progress and see how big the impact you are making is – individually as well as collectively with other people who care about making a difference – just like you.
descriptionHTML:
AWorld is the App for living sustainably in the modern world.

Created in support of ActNow - the United Nations campaign for individual action on climate change and sustainability.

Everyone has a role in the fight against climate change.
Join other people just like you

Let AWorld guide and inspire you in taking tangible, everyday actions towards living a sustainable lifestyle... completely FREE!

By changing your habits and making choices that have a less harmful impact on the environment, you have the power to confront the climate challenge and build a more sustainable world.
Here, you’ll find interactive and inspiring content to help you on your journey. You'll find tips, and challenges all geared towards making better choices part of your everyday life.

Come and learn about sustainability with our fun and gamified experience


In detail, AWorld offers:


- Journeys: Educational & inspiring content sorted in episodes to introduce you to sustainability, Sustainable Development Goals and stories about people committed in helping our planet

- Habits: Fun and sustainable actions you can take everyday. The App will act as a reminder and give you points for taking action.
For each action taken, the impact tracker will measure if it is water, CO2, energy or waste you are saving.


- Challenges: Groups of people that take matters into their own hands, and act for the planet. You can contribute to a challenge by taking and logging your actions. Challenges can also be sponsored by partners that pledge to make a sustainable donation if the community reaches the goal.


- Tips: Easy daily minute reads to help live a sustainable lifestyle.They come in a form of Weekly Trending topics that connect you to with what’s going on around the world

- Impact Tracker: This keeps track of your actions and shows you exactly how much your new lifestyle is saving

The points within AWorld measure progress towards living a sustainable lifestyle.
You can utilize points as markers of your own sustainability journey and accumulate points to uplevel to the next stage. In moving through levels by collecting points, you can see how your own habits and actions make an impact on our planet

By using this App, you’ll find a pathway to action, small steps that make a big difference, and inspiration for a new kind of power.

Join us and take action. Together with companies, organizations, and each other.
Because together is where real change happens.

You can track your progress and see how big the impact you are making is – individually as well as collectively with other people who care about making a difference – just like you.

title: SeenIt: Fashion Lifestyle App
description:
Say hello to SeenIt - India’s 1st fashion Q&A app where you simply post an image or look & let millions of stylists find shoppable answers. Our community of expert fashionistas is here to help you find all the fashion and lifestyle items you’re looking for. And the best part – its free!

Well, you can browse through our unlimited celebrity shoppable collections or ask anything using an image - including starting a poll to get real time honest answers. If you’re confused where to shop for a Sonam Kapoor outift that she wore for a movie promo, just post a photo of the look and let the experts make your shopping easier and quicker! You can whip out those fashion magazines, fashion apps and instagram blogger looks. Ask the community to help you track down the items you love. Moreover, you can follow your favourite fashion and lifestyle trends, celebrities and bloggers. Get inspired and find where to buy your favourite looks!

In The News
"You can find Outfits from Bollywood and Hollywood Movies and TV Shows. It’s a whole new world." - BuzzFeed
"Love something you’ve seen? Let this handy website track it down for you." - Little Black Book
"The Quora Of Fashion In India with over 500,000 monthly users." - Huffington Post
Whether you want that Alia Bhatt’s dress, or the earrings that Deepika Padukone wore for some award function, all you have to do is post that photo on SeenIt, and the users will tell you where to shop that look." - Indian Women Blog

Users Love Us
"This is a dream come true. Always knew I needed this in my life!" - Ms. R****a Kapoor
"Love this app with all the latest fashion trends to shop. Spend too much time browsing." - Ms. N****a Siroy
"Now I browse Instagram and Pinterest without stress. As soon as I see something I want and can't find it I post the image on SeenIt and their virtual stylists help me out" - Ms. So**** Mahajan

Is The Community For You?
This positive community consists of Bollywood celebrities, stylists, fashion and lifestyle bloggers and anyone who loves individual style and has a fancy for great design.

In case you were wondering, you can be the one giving advice too. Help fellow fashionistas discover the latest trends and share your answers, becoming an expert in the process! The feeling of knowing and the satisfaction of helping someone out by using your passion and skills without any monetary or physical reward, is priceless. Today, everything we do on the internet is selfish and it is rare to do something for someone else. So when you do it, it feels profound and rewarding. It may sound weird but give it a shot and you'll see for yourself.

You can also explore the world of fashion and lifestyle through several categories: Trends, bloggers, clothes, accessories, celebrities, and Movies & TV Series. Good luck organising such a full closet!

The newly introduced search function allows you to find the latest Bollywood and Hollywood celebrities and latest fashion trends such as: dresses, tops, skirts, gowns, tees, scarfs, sweatshirts, jeggings and design. You can also shop through the trending international and boutique fashion and lifestyle stores.

Anyway, we're getting back to finding more celeb style inspiration!

What should you do? You've heard and tried of some of the best fashion apps in India. Now its time to have the SeenIt experience!

For any suggestions/feedback email us at hello@seenit.in

title: Tinder - Dating, Make Friends and Meet New People
description:
🔥You can be here for a good time, and a long time, too.🔥 

With 30 billion matches to date, Tinder® is the🔝 top dating app🔝, making it the place to be to meet new people. Whether you’re looking for love, need a date today, or just want to chat: We’ve got something for local singles everywhere and features that give you the best dating experience possible. Like what? Glad you asked😉 

Whether you’re gay or bisexual, be proud of who you are with our Orientation feature🏳️‍🌈🏳️‍⚧️
Find out what you’ve got in common with your potential match with Interests🤝
Bring a plus one on all your dates for extra safety with Noonlight🛡️

Take us with you on your travels and get to know the locals — wherever you go, we’ll be there. Some people call us their “most dependable matchmaker”, some people call us 🔥the world’s most popular free dating app🔥, but you can just call us when you want to meet up with people in your area. 

🥂While you’re here — make a toast to the Gold life and enjoy all of Tinder’s premium features with our top-tier subscription🥂

Likes You allows you to see all your fans, saving you precious time🕰️ 
Unlimited Likes for you to catch feelings for as many people as you want💚
Rewind for you to undo your last Like or Nope⏪
Use Passporttm to go anywhere in the world to find people online outside your zip code✈️
Boost your profile to the top for thirty minutes to get more attention⚡
5 Super Likes per day because sometimes you really, really Like someone💝 

There’s a plus side for those not ready to commit to a relationship with 💛Gold 💛.  With Tinder Plus®, you’ll unlock features including Unlimited Likes, Passport, Rewind, Boost, and 5 Super Likes per day. 

Match. Chat. Date. That’s our mantra. It’s easy and fun to find people on Tinder. Make your profile stand out with your best pics and a little something about you to increase your match making potential. Use the 👉Swipe Right™👉 feature to Like someone, use the 👈Swipe Left™👈 feature to pass. If someone Likes you back, It’s a Match! And, there’s no pressure: We created the double opt-in which means two people have to show a mutual interest in order for there to be a match. How many dating apps can say that?🤔 

Tinder is the biggest and flyest party in the world for singles — it’s about time you showed up.🍾

-----------------------------------

If you choose to purchase Tinder Plus or Tinder Gold, payment will be charged to your Google Play account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in the Play Store after purchase. Current Tinder Plus subscription price starts at $9.99 USD/month, and one-month, 6-month and 12-month packages are available. Current Tinder Gold subscription price starts at $14.99 USD/month, and one-month, 6-month and 12-month packages are available. Prices are in U.S. dollars, may vary in countries other than the U.S. and are subject to change without notice. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period. If you don’t choose to purchase Tinder Plus or Tinder Gold, you can simply continue using Tinder for free.

All photos are of models and used for illustrative purposes only.

Privacy: https://www.gotinder.com/privacy
Terms: https://www.gotinder.com/terms

comments: Push notifications declaring I have matches and should start conversation only to get in and there's nothing. Either don't do the push notifications like that until they've been there a little, or if it's bugging, fix it; I don't mind if someone unmatches but I'd rather know that's why they're not showing up so I'm not left thinking the app is sabotaging it? Definitely wouldn't spend money on it like that.

Totally miserable experience. Repetitive match suggestions, they keep appearing even after I reject them. Overpriced super expensive extras. All my matches, conversations, media and settings were lost after a website update - I was unable to continue with my connections - no reaction from support. And that was a paid "gold" account! Complete waste of money, time and energy.

Wouldn't recommend. Dudes swipe right, in order to match but don't talk. It makes no sense. If you're interested in someone and match them, why be unresponsive? It is very immature and wastes everyone's time. Therefore I am giving a low rating. There's great potential, but people need to stop being immature and actually talk to their matches.

Installed the app and cannot log on either with Facebook, phone or email. Constant errors keep popping up when trying to log into an existing account. Edit October 2020. Since found out I have been banned from Tinder. When I spoke to them, they will not tell me why I have been banned and they didn't do appeals. How can you ban someone and not tell them why or to even get their side of the story!!!

Ive been on tinder acouple of times in the past and it was easy without and real problem or bug. I downloaded it again last night and it won't open and keeps saying "we're experiencing some issues". Who's messed around with it? I mean there's no actual chance of meeting anyone on there, but it was perfectly fine and straightforward before.

title: SmartHQ
description:
SmartHQ lets you manage and control a variety of smart Appliances from GE Appliances, GE Profile, Café, Monogram, and Haier to give you total control of your headquarters, your home. Now compatible with the New GE Profile Opal 2.0 Nugget Ice Maker (models XPIO13SCSS & XPIO13BCBT)!

Replaces Café Appliances app, Monogram app and GE Laundry app. 

KEY FEATURES
• REMOTE CONTROL – remotely monitor and control your SmartHQ enabled GE Appliances so you can do things like turn your oven on when you are heading home
• VOICE INTEGRATION – Select SmartHQ enabled Appliances work with both Amazon Alexa and Google Assistant -- now you can multi-task with ease!
• NOTIFICATIONS – Receive helpful alerts from your smart appliance that tell you when your oven is done pre-heating or if you left the refrigerator door open and many others
• SERVICE ALERTS – Get notified if your appliance needs attention
• SOFTWARE UPDATES - Keep your smart appliance up-to-date and access new features for your smart appliance as soon as they become available

COMPATIBILITY REQUIREMENTS: 
Requires a compatible GE SmartHQ enabled Refrigerator, Dishwasher, Wall Oven/Range, Washer, Dryer, or with a U+ Connect module. U+ Connect modules can be purchased online: https://www.geapplianceparts.com/store/parts/spec/PBX23W00Y0?SpecType=SpecType 

HELP AND SUPPORT
Have questions or need help getting connected? Contact:
• Phone: 1-800-220-6899
• E-Mail: connected@help.geappliances.com

recentChanges: Update includes enhancements to the appliance setup process, capability for in-app reviews, and an universal replenishment feature for all connected dishwashers
comments: Super opaque app that took forever to set up. It spun for literal minutes before connecting. Then in trying to send feedback -- which I was prompted to do -- I got a 501 error. Not implemented?! My gas cooktop is off (I'm standing in front of it), but the app says it's on, and has some sort of animation which I'd normally expect to be some kind of "refresh" animation. There's no excuse for this kind of sloppiness in 2020.

Simply can't connect to the appliance.... This app is ridiculous. It uses the same idiotic system used by Honeywell in which you have to connect to their Wi-Fi signal and jump through all these hoops. No matter what you do it still won't work because apparently it can't find your appliance in the cloud. This is a classic example of software engineers building something without any user testing or input. I fail to understand why companies can't just get this simple thing right.

First, you're required to register and give up a lot of personal information right upfront. I hated it. It should have delayed all of these nosy questions until the app actually has a reason, like for a service appointment. Second, the temperature settings in the app disagree with what the front controls on the fridge show. I ended up disabling the wifi on the fridge. The bottom line, it should be more anonymous and reliable. The reply shows total ignorance, so it's a cultural issue as well.

Horrible this app doesn't allow for anything i go through the motion of registering my appliances on the ge website. I download this app to control them and still nothing. The website says what you should be able to to do on the app but that's not the case here. I dont understand why they would launch an app before they work out all the kinks.

So aggravating! I have been in touch with GE's support team, through phone calls and e-mail, well over a MONTH. No luck getting appliances connected. (A dishwasher & water softener.) So, doing some research, I found out that anything that can only utilize the 2.4 band on the router (such as this app requires) is what causes the problem with an IP address not getting assigned, or it being "found in the cloud". Also read somewhere this app doesn't work with the new mesh systems. GE, really???
