title: My Principal® Lifestyle
description:
Thanks for trusting us to protect your loved ones with life insurance. To make a payment, participate in wellness challenges, and more, download this app.

Getting started is easy:
1. Download the app, create an account and sync your fitness tracker or fitness app
2. Get points when you achieve goals, complete challenges and more

If you are a Principal life insurance policyholder you will see your policy(ies) and have the ability to maintain them. 

Visit the app regularly to:
• See how many points you have
• Manage your goals and start more challenges
• Check on and maintain your beneficiaries 
• Make policy payments

Eventually you will be able to make a name, address or email change among other policy related transactions. “That all sounds great,” you say, “but what about my privacy?” The fact is, we value it greatly. That’s why we won’t sell your data – ever. 

Get started with My Principal® Lifestyle today to maintain both your financial and physical wellness.
descriptionHTML:
Thanks for trusting us to protect your loved ones with life insurance. To make a payment, participate in wellness challenges, and more, download this app.

Getting started is easy:
1. Download the app, create an account and sync your fitness tracker or fitness app
2. Get points when you achieve goals, complete challenges and more

If you are a Principal life insurance policyholder you will see your policy(ies) and have the ability to maintain them.

Visit the app regularly to:
• See how many points you have
• Manage your goals and start more challenges
• Check on and maintain your beneficiaries
• Make policy payments

Eventually you will be able to make a name, address or email change among other policy related transactions. “That all sounds great,” you say, “but what about my privacy?” The fact is, we value it greatly. That’s why we won’t sell your data – ever.

Get started with My Principal® Lifestyle today to maintain both your financial and physical wellness.

comments: I tried to use this to track my workouts. Huge fail! I am connected to Garmin, Strava and Google Fit for sharing. All of these apps will update one from another, except this app. It's not worth the effort.

This is a great app. Keeps me motivated,  has challenges & is in  sync with my fitness device. Haven't figured out how to sync for elliptical work outs yet, though, or stairs.  Earn points redeemable for gift cards! Maybe someday will be redeemable for discounts on life insurance premium.

Great app.  Helps me stay on track with attainable challenges and reachable rewards.  It makes me want to meet my goals to get the points even if I don't want to so I can get my next gift card reward.

This app gives you the opportunity to be rewarded for exercise that you're already doing and provides incentives to walk/climb/bike more for extra points. It can take a while for points to accumulate but I've been able to redeem my points for $50 worth of gift cards so far. If you have a fitness tracker you might as well use this app too and earn rewards.

This app makes it easy to earn small rewards for living a healthy lifestyle.  Customer service is very responsive on questions.  My Garmin automatically sends my steps to the app, so it's almost effortless.

title: Freeletics Training Coach – Bodyweight & Mindset
description:
Europe’s #1 fitness app lets you work out anytime, anywhere with the best digital personal trainer - no gym required. Whatever your fitness level, achieve your goals quickly and build healthy habits with personalized HIIT workouts and audio coaching. Losing weight, gaining muscle or improving your fitness has never been so simple. 

WHY FREELETICS? 
- Freeletics means freedom. Work on yourself and your fitness free of excuses like time, equipment, space, money or know-how. Join 42 million others doing their workout whenever and wherever they want. 
- See fast results with the most advanced digital personal trainer and effective HIIT workouts. Your AI personal trainer tailors everything to you, learning from each exercise and piece of feedback to create your perfect workout, every time. No two people get the same workout plan - this is fully personalized fitness.
- We follow a holistic approach to fitness and self-development. We combine HIIT fitness, mindfulness, knowledge and motivation to help you perfect your training and build a strong foundation for life-long positive change.
 
The free version of the app contains 20 HIIT bodyweight workouts, 25 exercises, 20 audio sessions, workout spots and a community of millions. If you want to set yourself up for long-term success with the guidance of a personal trainer every step of the way, you can sign up for the Freeletics Coach with a 14-day money back guarantee. 


What you get by upgrading to the Freeletics Coach:

TRAINING 
- Enjoy your own AI-powered personal trainer, who puts every HIIT workout together based on your experience, goals, fitness level and preferences.
- Travelling or short on time? Need to be quiet? Stuck without equipment or can’t go for a run? No problem. Tell your personal trainer what’s going on and it will adapt your workout to suit your needs.
- Your workout plan will be compiled in a “Training Journey.” Choose from 20 Training Journeys in the app, each with a different fitness focus. Look out for our limited editions by professional athletes.
- Choose your workout style. Whether it’s running, bodyweight HIIT or weights in the gym - or a combination of these - there’s a Training Journey for you. Fitness will never be boring again.
- Progress in your training with thousands of HIIT workout variations and over 180 exercises.

The Training Coach is included in the Training, Training & Nutrition and Body & Mind bundles.


MINDSET
- Add audio coaching to your personal trainer, helping you build a strong, balanced mindset and find lasting motivation to improve your health and fitness. The perfect complement to your HIIT workouts.
- In 5 to 20-minute sessions, learn how to build habits, boost weight loss, de-stress and improve your focus, training, recovery and sleep. The perfect foundation for real success.
- Courses include focus, stress, sleep, fitness, nutrition and motivation.

The Mindset Coach is only included in the Body & Mind bundle.


SUBSCRIPTIONS AND TERMS
We offer 8 auto-renewing subscription options:
- Training (3 / 6 / 12 months)
- Training & Nutrition (3 / 6 / 12 months)
- Body & Mind (3 / 12 months)
 
The Nutrition Coach is part of the Freeletics Nutrition app.

By purchasing, you accept our Terms of Use (https://www.freeletics.com/en/pages/terms/) and Privacy Policy (https://www.freeletics.com/en/pages/privacy/).
 
Contact us at support@freeletics.com or follow @Freeletics on social media for daily workout inspiration. Your personal trainer is ready when you are. Happy training.

recentChanges: We squashed some bugs. Let us know if you find more. Our developers will fix them faster than you can do an Aphrodite.
comments: I went to the gym for years but I have achieved the best shape of my body thanks to this app! It gives you the motivation, discipline and helps you build the proper technique. I would never imagine an app being that much effective. Instead of paying crazy amounts to the gym, you should download this app and enjoy sessions at the comfort of your home or by the sea or in a park

Updates spoilt the workouts. Pull ups became monkey pull ups. Stretches became a bunch of stuff that need equipment such as bars and benches to complete. The main workouts are still good. The demonstration of the workouts became poorer. With more technique required for stretches, I think they need to add a "it was too difficult, I couldn't do it" option. If you don't have the mobility required, it is a matter of just waiting for the time to past.

Really cool app! I enjoy the training so far. The only thing is that you can't say you can't do XY exercise for XY reason. So you're stuck by saying you completed the exercise but you didn't perform well. Or try hitting the "adapt session" button and create a hole new training for the day while I only wanted to change 1 exercise.

Always exactly the same exercises day after day, week after week. Lunges, squats, lunges, squats, reverse lunges, cossack squats... its harrowing to say the least, my knees feel like i may as well be 78 in the shade they click more and more each day because this app thinks that leg day is every f#@$%ng day. Tried a different training journey using weights, and the first thing they asked me to do was, surprise, lunges with the himalayan mountain range resting on my shoulders. Ffs im a beginner.

*FREE*Letics?... So I entered my goals, height, age etc and opted for the free version. I was given a workout programme which looks perfect for what I need (Hybrid Strength), only to then be made to pay to see the exercises and details? Absolute joke

title: Daymmy - Lifestyle Tracker
description:
You will be able to evaluate and modify your lifestyle with Daymmy.
Answer the questions and analyze the results within different periods.
Observe the dynamics of your indicators and compare yourself with other users.

🚀How does it work?

✔ Step one. You set up a personal profile, choose questions from the gallery or create your own.
✔ Step two. The application at the appointed time proposes to answer the selected questions.
✔ Step three. When the application has accumulated enough data, you can:
- see the dynamics of indicators on visual graphs;
- understand which of the indicators affect each other;
- compare your results with the average results of other users.

📱Examples of daily questions
- How did you sleep?
- What did you do today?
- Estimate your day eventfulles
- How is your mood today?
- What time did you wake up today?

📊Why Daymmy?

🔸The application allows the most flexible configuration of the questionnaire. Choose questions from the gallery or add your own questions with any type of answer.
🔹If the charts in the application are not enough for you, you can always upload data to spreadsheets and analyze them in any aspect;
🔸We do not have ads;
🔹We created an application that we use ourselves.

comments: This app constantly freezes when I go to use it. When I try to access it the app doesnt load. When I am able to access it the content is fab!

I've been an RWL member for 5 years and I LOVE it. So many varieties of workouts and recipes that it's almost impossible to get bored. I find the app very easy to use, it's set out simple and straightforward and even has a feature where you can track your progress. If you haven't downloaded it yet, what are you waiting for?!

I love this app! Is everything I need to help me achieve and maintain my diet and exercise goals; 1000s of healthy tasty recipes and diet styles, personalised macro calculations, 1000s fun and varied workouts, trainers who are so positive and familiar they almost feel like friends. Speaking of friends the community message board is what sets this app apart from others. Couldn't live without this app now, the subscription fee is worth every penny, just wish I'd joined sooner xx

It's hard to put into words how fantastic this app, the rwl plans, workouts, recipes and community is. I've lost 1 stone in 1 month, have made incredibly supportive new friends, am so much more confident in my own skin and am starting to love the body I'm in. It's so much more than a workout programme and I would encourage anyone to give it a try, you really won't regret it!
Can't unsubscribe!!!! This app is a scam. It won't allow me to unsubscribe as you cannot follow any of the instructions to cancel membership and they do not offer refunds!!!

title: XOJON Lifestyle
description:
XOJON顛覆大家對於運動空間的緊繃想像。
這裡有專業的幼兒體適能與球類教學，從小培養孩子的運動協調能力，更秉持破除填鴨式教育的理念，讓孩子在0至6歲的黃金成長時期中，能夠盡情自我探索，使各方面能力都能有最完整的發展。除此之外，也有提供成人瑜珈以及器械式彼拉提斯課程，讓大人小孩都能養成規律的運動習慣，還有專業的筋膜放鬆師在安靜的空間裡為你伸展，讓身心靈達到最極致的放鬆。


課程介紹I：SPORTS RIDER 小騎士兒童運動課程

體操課程規劃：
Lv1：親子班      適合年齡：1歲10個月～3歲
Lv2：幼幼體操  適合年齡：3歲～4歲6個月      
Lv3：幼童體操  適合年齡：4歲6個月～6歲
針對學前幼兒，訓練基本運動能力，發展敏捷度、平衡感、協調性，縮短專項運動項目學習曲線

幼童球類規劃：
1.籃球 
2.網球
3.桌球
4.足球
由專項教練訓練小學員對球類的基本觀念與動作，發展運動興趣，學習團體合作精神。

課程介紹II：成人課程

1.器械式皮拉提斯：
皮拉提斯教室設有8台皮拉提斯核心床(Balanced Body reformer)，幫助改善不良姿勢、強化深層核心肌肉群、雕塑緊緻身體曲線。

2.瑜珈：
以緩和漸進的體位法練習為主，在平穩均勻的呼吸中逐步引導身體延伸、放鬆肌肉組織，讓各部位都能獲得舒展。

3.空中瑜伽：
運用懸垂的絹布，藉助地心引力與布的螺旋力，使平時難以完成的瑜珈動作變得較輕鬆，幫助身體獲得深層的舒展與釋放緊繃壓力。

會員專屬服務專區：

休息區提供咖啡、面膜販售、雞蛋糕與精緻餐點給會員享用，讓會員在運動過後，能放心享用健康的美食。


核心平衡伸展 :
透過伸展達到筋膜放鬆，迎接更有活力的身體。


查看更多詳情，請訪問XOJON的官方網站：
xojonlifestyle.com


系統及技術支援由BookFast POS智能場館系統顧問提供。

title: Evergo
description:
Evergo integrates and brings forth all of your lifestyle needs, into one cohesive and user friendly application. It allows you to use a simple interface to digitally and virtually book appointments, classes, slots or otherwise for all your daily needs. Instead of using multiple applications, making numerous phone calls, and trying to find time to do it all, Evergo does it all for you!
Evergo has everything that you will need to plan out your day, effectively! We aim to cater to a rather diverse and broad market segment in terms of providing customers with all that they need on a single platform.
It can be used as a very powerful service comparison tool. This will allow users to browse through different businesses whilst simultaneously comparing services, prices, locations and otherwise. This customizable feature allows you, as a customer to find exactly what you’re looking for at a certain moment in time.
Being an application that provides various different services, across diverse markets, Evergo is extremely powerful in terms of productivity and efficiency, where it speeds up the process of booking, and decreases any risk of miscommunication in terms of timings and services required. The application becomes an effective communication channel between a customer and the vendor; through which customer satisfaction is guaranteed.

title: Stilpunkte Lifestyle Guide
description:
Mit der STILPUNKTE-APP vom Online-Portal www.stilpunkte.de sind erstklassige Adressen, exklusive Angebote und exzellente Produktinspirationen nur noch einen Finger-Tipp entfernt. Die STILPUNKTE Ihrer Stadt zeigen wir im gewohnt stilsicheren Design jetzt für das iPhone optimiert und mit der GPS-unterstützten „STILPUNKTE IN DEINER NÄHE“-Funktion sichern wir auch Ihr spontanes Shopping-Vergnügen – einfach, übersichtlich, stilvoll.

STILPUNKTE ist als Life-Style-Guide stets auf der Suche nach ausschließlich außergewöhnlichen Adressen in Ihrer Stadt. Entdecken Sie stilsicher kulinarische Genüsse, ausgefallene Einrichtungs- und Gestaltungstipps, neueste Mode-, Schönheits- und Wellnesstrends, einzigartiges Schmuck- und Uhrendesign, Kunst in ausgewählten Galerien und Highlights rund um Autos und „Mobiles“.

Unsere top-aktuellen STILPUNKTE auf dem iPhone stellen wir in Köln, Düsseldorf, Bonn/Rhein-Sieg, Essen/Ruhrgebiet, Koblenz, Aachen, sowie im Bergische Land und im Niederrhein vor. Weitere Städte/Regionen folgen.

title: Urbanologie - lifestyle guide
description:
There’s a whole lot for U to discover with Urbanologie, your constant lifestyle and travel companion. Be the first in the know and discover up-to-minute insider news about all of the new hip hangouts, pop-ups, unmissable events and the most anticipated restaurant, bar, club and hotel openings; discover interactive editorials featuring insider knowledge, from recommending the best tables to signature dishes and access daily updated editorial content as selected by in-house editors, local contributors and influencers. Discover the world according to U in London, New York, Miami, Dubai, Los Angeles & Beyond. 

• Discover up-to-minute insider news about all of the new hip hangouts, pop-ups, unmissable events and the most anticipated restaurant, bar, club and hotel openings – in each destination that we cover. 
• Discover interactive editorials featuring insider knowledge, from recommending the best tables to signature dishes.

title: Calm - Meditate, Sleep, Relax
description:
Calm is a leading app for meditation and sleep. Join the millions experiencing lower stress, less anxiety, and more restful sleep with our guided meditations, Sleep Stories, breathing programs, masterclasses, and relaxing music. Recommended by top psychologists, therapists, and mental health experts.

Calm is the perfect mindfulness app for beginners, but also includes hundreds of programs for intermediate and advanced users.

Guided meditation sessions are available in lengths of 3, 5, 10, 15, 20 or 25 minutes so you can choose the perfect length to fit with your schedule. Topics include:

* Calming Anxiety
* Managing Stress
* Deep Sleep
* Focus and Concentration
* Relationships
* Breaking Habits
* Happiness
* Gratitude
* Self-Esteem
* Body Scan
* Loving-Kindness
* Forgiveness
* Non-judgement
* Commuting to work or school
* Mindfulness at College
* Mindfulness at Work
* Walking meditation
* Calm Kids
* And so much more...

Also featuring:

* An original Daily Calm every day: a new 10-minute program added daily to help ease you into the day or unwind with before bed
* 100+ Sleep Stories: adult bedtime stories guaranteed to lull you to sleep
* 7 and 21 day programs for both beginner and advanced users
* Life-changing Calm Masterclasses taught by world-renowned experts
* Breathing exercises to help you relax
* Exclusive music engineered to help you focus, relax or sleep
* Unguided timed meditation
* Open-ended meditation
* 30+ soothing nature sounds and scenes to use during meditation, yoga or to help you sleep

Track your progress with:

* Daily streaks
* Time spent meditating

Calm is loved by the press:

* “I’m generally wary of meditation apps because they sometimes weave in too much mystic talk for my taste. But Calm instead contains guidance like ‘Concentrate on your body’” - New York Times

* “In the frenetic, crazy, digital world we live in, sometimes it's necessary to take a step back and smell the roses” - Mashable

* “Eliminating distraction...ended up helping me relax and realize that all the stuff I was stressing about wasn't that big a deal” - Tech Republic

* “Found myself similarly refreshed afterwards” - TechCrunch

Calm is free to download and use, and there are no ads. A subset of the programs and features are free forever.

Some content is only available through an optional paid subscription. If you choose to subscribe, payment will be charged to your Google Account at confirmation of purchase.

comments: I have used this app for over 4 years! I had the free version for a year and a half and loved it but wanted a little more. I use the paid version now. It doesn't cost anymore than any streaming service, actually cheaper than my Netflix and even Hulu. I'd give up both for this app if I had to. Helps with my sleep , my kid's sleep and our mental growth. I highly recommend using this!

Stopped before I even started. This app expects you not only to have to sign in and create an account straight away, but the "free" trial also requires you to sign up with an active credit card before you even get to experience anything. I personally hate this way of working and tend to turn away from all apps that insist on this model. Installed and deleted within ten minutes.

11th month update: Now I am trying to delete my subscription it is sooooo difficult. Unbelievable. I would never recommend this app. They have hidden the subscription change, created many bugs like your browser does not support... I am trying to unsubscribe using the app itself, but surprisingly it is not working because of java or smtng. Why you would need java to unsubscribe. You are trying to rob the users. Making it difficult so that they will give up, and you will continue making money

I tried the 7 days free trial and i found the meditation offered quite poor. Mostly too short and way too much talking, and not even in a soft spoken tone. I couldn't play any of its music in the background. Maybe my fault, but ok, since a lot of the music on offer is pop commercial singer stuff. I also didn't like the 'well done, set a reminder' type of approach. A meditation app should provide escape from the manic, 'like' addictive type of world, not mimic it. Disappointed

This app changed my life. It really helped me became a calmer person and have clarity. My mind is much more peaceful and have significantly less troubling and negative thoughts, even when I do have them sometimes, I'm able to distinguish them as just thoughts and not my reality. This is a really helpful app and I'm so thankful to the creators and all those who worked hard to get it working as good as it is.

title: Flipboard - Latest News, Top Stories & Lifestyle
description:
Discover quality content for all your interests - from personalized news, entertainment, tech and sports articles to trending lifestyle magazines. We'll deliver the latest headlines, events, and entertainment stories to save you time, keep you informed and make sure you're always up-to-date with what's happening.

NEW: Flipboard TV - watch video from hundreds of publishers, TV stations and independent producers for free. Visit the Explore tab to select from 20 curated video channels for news, politics, travel, lifestyle, celebrity, sports and more.

Trust our unique combination of professional editors and smart algorithms to customize and deliver must-read stories and undiscovered gems. Get the full perspective on the latest news - and share what you find. Our editors blend expert voices and curated sources, and even recommended stories they know you'll like, so you can sit back and flip through what matters most to you. 

You can even customize your personalized newsstand: pick your passions and create a Smart Magazine for each topic feed. Are you interested in world news, events or tech developments? Want to read articles from national newspapers, discover sports podcasts, and skim the latest news? Looking to seize the zeitgeist from trending lifestyle stories? Flipboard has you covered. 

Plus, you can create personal magazines: find articles you want to read later or you want to share, and use the "+" to flip them into your own magazines. 

MAKE THE BEST USE OF YOUR TIME ON FLIPBOARD:

• Discover the latest news from The New York Times, National Geographic, Vanity Fair, and thousands more top newspapers and magazines, local, national or from around the world

• Create and customize your Smart Magazines: bundle together sources, people and even hashtags to get access to truly personalized news

• Customize your home feed: collate up to 9 of your favorite Smart Magazines together for quick access to the features you love

• Read The Daily Edition: keep up with the latest headlines and trending events in our daily roundup of important stories and personalized news articles

• Curate your perspective: collect stories around specific themes and add them to personal magazines

TOP PUBLISHERS ON FLIPBOARD:

- News & Politics: discover the latest headlines in national and world news, with newspapers and publications like The New York Times, CNN, Politico, Axios
- Tech & Science: read the latest tech news with TechCrunch, trending science stories with Wired, and more
- Business & Entrepreneurship: get personalized news relevant to your interests from The Wall Street Journal, Bloomberg, Forbes
- Sports: national pastimes or world news, never miss key sporting events with ESPN, CBS Sports
- Entertainment: get world news, even for celebrities and entertainment with People, Rolling Stone, Variety
- Lifestyle & Wellness: explore emerging lifestyle trends with Brit + Co., Self, Women's Health
- Food & Cooking: get some serious food inspiration from Bon Appetit, Food & Wine, Serious Eats
- Travel: feed your wanderlust with National Geographic, Travel + Leisure, Lonely Planet
- Home & Gardening: dream up your ideal home ELLE DECOR, House Beautiful
- Style: avant-garde or corporate with an edge... get sartorial inspiration from Vogue, Refinery29, W Magazine, GQ

KEEP UP WITH FLIPBOARD:

For product updates and the latest headlines from our blog, including tips on how to use Flipboard and interviews with actors, writers, musicians, and more. Follow us on:
www.twitter.com/@flipboard
www.facebook.com/Flipboard
https://www.linkedin.com/company/flipboard-inc-

For videos on how to use Flipboard, visit https://about.flipboard.com/tutorials/

Need help using the Flipboard app? Browse our help articles by opening Settings then Help & Feedback. Or, click the contact button at flip.it/help

comments: Nice interface. Though each type of device has a different user experience, (iOS, Android, MacOS), a little weird but each is still very good. I like the ability to add and subtract areas if interest. They mark ads/sponsored posts pretty well. Pretty speedy on all devices, even somewhat older ones. Overall a nice news agragator.

I've been using flipboard for years. Now like 80% of the content is videos. And NONE of those videos actually play. It's so weird. They have some new video set up, every time I click on a video, it doesn't play. Just black screen. Click on it, it goes to another black screen. So, two major problems rendering this app useless: 1. Nearly all news is now in the form of videos. I don't want videos. I want to read, and 2. Those videos don't even work. How do you not beta test this, Flipboard??

If I open a page on source like golf or mma or something like that, I get articles that cover something else entirely. I'm really annoyed that I spend more time reporting articles that are not on topic and I don't know why this hasn't changed in years of reporting these articles... Please do something about this.

Been using flipboard for quite some time since you can customize what news you see or just flip through all news. Biggest down side is tbe comment section is really subpar and broken up into different sections. Dont even bother commenting if you see 100 plus comments because your comment is lost at the bottom. Other than that is a nice app to see any news you want.

Can't share URL if you click a link inside an article. Steps to repro: 1. Tap into an article 2. Tap any link on the page that goes to a different site 3. Observe the top toolbar shrinks from several items to 2 items. 4. Tap the share button in that toolbar 5. Pick literally anything on share sheet. 6. See "Couldn't Share item" error every time. If you fix this bug lmk and I'll revise my review! Update: Flipboard denied this obvious, reproducible bug. Smh. Bug does not happen on ios.

title: Fasting App - Fasting Tracker & Intermittent Fast
description:
Fasting Tracker will guide you to a new lifestyle with healthy habits. You’ll lose weight effectively and feel more active! No diet and no yo-yo effect.

IS IT EFFECTIVE?
It’s proven that intermittent fasting leads to fast weight loss. During fasting, as your glycogen depletes, your body switches to ketosis, which is referred to as the body's "fat-burning" mode. This is an effective way to burn fat.

IS IT SAFE?
Yes. It’s the most natural and safe way to lose weight. Studies show that eating all the time makes your body unable to take a break from digesting, which can result in health problems, such as diabetes. When you fast, you just take a break from eating, it takes some of the load off your liver.

CAN I USE FASTING TRACKER?
With various fasting plans, fasting tracker is suitable for beginner and experienced, men and women. It guides you through your plan. No need to change your diet, you can easily stick to it. If you are under 18 years old, pregnant or breastfeeding, have health issues or are underweight, please ask your doctor for advice before fasting.

WHY INTERMITTENT FASTING?
√ Burn your body fat reserves
√ Start the process of regeneration and detox during fasting
√ Slow down the aging process
√ Benefit for controlling blood sugar
√ Reduce inflammation
√ Prevent numerous diseases, such as heart diseases and diabetes
√ Boost your growth hormone and increase metabolism
√ Make you feel healthier and more active
√ Improve your body and brain function
√ The most natural way to lose weight and keep fit
√ Lose weight without diet and exercise

FEATURES OF FASTING TRACKER
√ Various intermittent fasting plans
√ For both beginner and experienced
√ One tap to start/end
√ Customize fasting plan
√ Adjust fasting/eating period
√ Set notifications for fasting
√ Smart fasting tracker
√ Fasting timer
√ Track your weight
√ Check fasting status
√ Science-based tips and articles about fasting
√ No need to count calories intake
√ Losing weight has become so easy
√ Sync data with Google Fit

SCIENTIFICALLY PROVEN INTERMITTENT FASTING

Effectively Lose Weight
Your body switches into fat burning mode. You’ll burn body fat reserves and prevent food you eat from being stored as fat.

Natural and Healthy
When fasting, your body will actively burn fat, get into detox mode and start the process of regeneration.

Detox
Your body reduces inflammation. Cells break down viruses, bacteria and damaged components.

Prevent Diseases
Studies show that fasting can prevent numerous diseases, such as heart diseases, diabetes and cancer.

Cell Repair and Regenerate
Cells remove unnecessary or dysfunctional components. Damaged cells will be replaced with stronger ones.

Against Aging
Your body initiates autophagy, a process of detoxification, repair and regeneration. This has benefits against aging.

Control Blood Sugar
Fasting helps you become more sensitive to insulin. It’s beneficial for controlling blood sugar.

Increase Metabolism
During fasting, your growth hormone goes up, and your metabolism will be increased.

comments: Been using it for a little over a month or so. I have such difficulty sticking with fasting, but this app has really helped keep me accountable, plus it's simple and there's not a ton of ads or "extra features" in your face. The overlay timer is a great constant reminder, and I like the water reminders. Only improvement I'd want is an option for the timer to be counting down and not up.

Just started using this app yesterday, but I really like it so far! Best feature I've found is that you can totally customize the amount of water you're drinking. There are so many different sizes nowadays that the ability to adjust the number of ounces makes a big difference. I also love that it tells you what's happening at each stage of fasting throughout the day!

This was the second fasting app I installed, and the one I've stuck with. It's convenient, easy to track, and has most of the features I'm looking for. Previously I gave 5 stars because it seemed to be missing actual start and stop times in the history. But the feature is there, I just missed it. User interface could be improved to make that more obvious. It's a great app and works offline too. This is likely the fasting tracker I will stick with.

I really like the app, it's exactly what I was looking for. It says pay 2.99 for ad removal, but honestly I haven't experienced any ads, besides a very rare one up top. My only complaint would be the subscription, I would pay for it if it was a one time purchase, but I'm not interested in getting a subscription to an app, sorry! 5 stars anyway because the free material does it's job.

I like this app and I appreciate it. Just I have paid $2.99 for ads-removed from the app but the app still shows the ads and ask me to pay again for removing Ads!! I have already sent an email to the developer but I didn't get the response! I'm waiting for your reply as soon as possible. I appreciate your help and support. title: Lifestyle Tracker
description:
Created by: Meenal Drock & Garry

Lifestyle Tracker is an app that will allow you to track the most important activities that your body needs to lead a healthy life. It is not a regular health tracker app that focuses all your energy on counting calories. Lifestyle Tracker helps you to create a healthy lifestyle for yourself by reminding you to do important things that your body needs daily. Once your lifestyle is on track, it automatically gets your body to maintain calories. 

Why do you need Lifestyle Tracker to remind you? That is because we want you to concentrate on your daily work life while the app takes care of your health and notifies when its time to eat, sleep, wake up, drink water, green tea, exercise and recommendations by experts.  You do not have to spend time to find the right things that you need to do in a day to live a healthy life. The app provides you information on everything you need to live a healthy lifestyle and stay on track!

Let's be practical. How many hours do you spend everyday just to watch what you eat and note down the calories in your fitness apps? And to be honest, you cannot enter calories every time you eat something because it is a hassle. Everyone is thinking about calories counting but if you dive deep you will realize that your calories will automatically be on track if you follow a healthy life by eating regularly and on time, getting 8 hours sleep, exercising daily, drinking water and green tea for a high metabolism. We make this easier for you by reminding you on timely basis based on expert recommendations for all important things your body needs daily.

Most of the fitness apps today concentrate on tracking calories count and entering food you intake.  But you need someone to remind you to do all the things that will help you maintain those calories. With this app you will concentrate your energy on eating, sleeping, exercising on time and the end result will be more than what you get through regular fitness apps. Once you get your daily schedule on track via lifestyle app, your fitness apps can be an addition and help you gain more results. You do not need to diet nor you need to invest time watching what you eat every minute, all you need to do is follow the routine when the app reminds you. 

This app is especially built for office goers who are stuck on their desks for long hours and are so busy that at times they do not realize that they are not drinking enough cups of water throughout the day. While you are at work, this app gives you a soft reminder so that you do not ignore your body in your busy life.

There are more than 100 things you can do in a day to lead a healthy life but do we have the time to do all of those? We hear you. That is why we have given you the most important reminder tiles by default and have set reminders based on expert recommendations so that you are on your way to lead a good lifestyle. If you hear of more things that you think could help you in long term, then you are covered. We allow you to add additional reminders for things that you would like to set by your own. 

Our ultimate goal is to ensure that every individual creates a lifestyle for himself which includes important things to be completed from morning till night and follows it regularly. That's what we call as maintaining a healthy lifestyle. Once you are used to living a lifestyle where you do everything on schedule then your body and mind is trained in that direction. Then you will automatically lead a good life. Allow us to remind you while you are on your way to track your lifestyle!

title: Compassion Lifestyle
description:
Träna din hjärna i välmående:
Compassion Lifestyle Appen innehåller mental träning för att träna hjärnan i positiva känslor och skapa inre trygghet för att må bra. Genom att göra övningarna lär du dig hur du kan må bra utifrån ett förhållningssätt av compassion som ny stresshanteringsmetod. 

Compassion bygger på forskning:
Forskning har visat att om man kan göra sin hjärna trygg och sin kropp lugn så förbättras vår hälsa och vår förmåga till koncentration, uthållighet, kreativitet samt planeringsförmåga. Genom att aktivera kroppens egna trygghetssystem skapas en buffert mot stress och möjliggör en känsla av livsglädje, bättre hälsa och goda relationer.

Kunskapen kring Compassion Lifestyle Appen bygger på hjärnforskning, KBT, affektteori, anknytningsteori, buddhism och mindfulness.

Appen med övningarna ingår i ett forskningsprojekt om compassion vid Karolinska Institutet.

Kunskapen kring Compassion Lifestyle Appen bygger på hjärnforskning, KBT, affektteori, anknytningsteori, buddhism och mindfulness.

Appen med övningarna ingår i ett forskningsprojekt om compassion vid Karolinska Institutet.
summary: The app trains the brain in positive emotions and creates internal security to feel good.

title: Healthy Lifestyle Guide
description:
Healthy Lifestyle Guide provides five steps to get better healthy life: 
Tips on Eating Style, Positive Mindset, Fitness, Habits, Skincare. 

This app will help you to change your current lifestyle (if in a negative way) to a better one. Also, it can be a solution for those who are having personality and health problems. 
Initially, we will guide you with changing your eating style to a healthy one, including carbs, portion needed, drink a lot and types of saturated fats. Next, this app emphasizes the way of your thinking and helps you to become a positive person. Some references for workout and loss weight also provided in this app, so you can click the link of any instructor according to the program you like. If you like this app, please rate us with a positive rating and do recommend to your family, friends and others. That will allow us to continue improving. Thank you for your cooperation.

title: Lifestyle Tips
description:
Our body is our temple and we need to take care of it. Do you know that over 70% of Americans are either obese or overweight?[1] That’s insane! Think of your body as your physical shell to take you through life. If you repeatedly abuse it, your shell will wear out quickly.

Life is beautiful and you don’t want to bog yourself down with unnecessary health problems. Today, your vital organs may be working well, but they may not be tomorrow. Don’t take your health for granted. Take proper care of your body.

title: African Dresses
description:
In this African Dresses App, we have trendy African dress styles for African Women.

App Features

#Unique African Fashion Styles
#Kente Fashion Styles
#Urban African clothing design
#Ghanaian African wear styles
#African Print long dress styles
#African Kids Fashion

The African print has developed to become an amazing fashion statement in the modern world. It’s in the beauty of the natural prints and also the graceful appeal of various African dresses that have created this fashion craze. So if you are looking for an impressive and sexy way to step out in style then these modern African dress styles will ensure you can’t go wrong. Experiment and find the African fashion style that most appeals to you.

Best Beautiful and Lovely Collection of African Dresses

African clothing design has been embraced by western fashion due to its creativity and sophistication, which have been introduced by many great African designers. The beauty of the garments they create lies in their uniqueness and style, which does not misplace its culture, spirit or nature. There are many distinctive aspects of African fashion design that make it simply incredible and very original, bringing a part of African culture with every garment.

African dresses come in all styles, patterns and designs. Beautifully crafted Ankara styles are all you need this summer. African print clothes always look amazing when worn in the right fashion. African Dresses app features different latest styles of African Ankara patch work designs and fashion styles that you can choose from, and be inspired to create your own design that will definitely make you stand out.

Ankara designs and fashion styles seem to be renewed every day as we always see new styles popping up with unlimited designs that are worth styling and flaunting.One of the hottest trends is the Ankara patch design, that is done by infusing Ankara prints into other fabric to give a unique and elegant customize style.

African Attire for Women

These African clothing for women are the right attire to transform your look and boost your confidence this season. Our African dresses for women will make and stand out in any formal occasion, party, wedding, religious event, home-coming, African history month or family reunion.

African print wrap dresses are currently in trend. The fabric used to make the dress makes it all the more beautiful. Skater dresses made with print fabrics are quite beautiful. Latest African fashion dresses are simply fabulous! African style has fascinated and conquered the taste of numerous fashion designers and remain sophisticated outfits of modern fashionistas. Let's find out the top African fashion dresses.

Fashion trends of African dresses

African fashion style is undoubtedly the best one to take inspiration from. The attractiveness of African fashion dresses for ladies cannot leave anyone indifferent. African style of dress is considered to be the most vivid and recognizable among other varieties of ethnic styles.

Modern African dresses styles are distinguished by their wonderful and fascinating patterns. African landscapes, plants, images of wild animals and colors that complement our skin tones are often used as patterns for African fabrics.

Rate us and Write a Feedback

title: Haply - Mood Tracker
description:
Haply allows you to track how you are feeling throughout your day. It is everything you need to chart your emotional/mental fluctuations and help you understand your emotions better.

Haply gives you personal insights to what your habits do to your lifestyle and figure out patterns that can make you happier or more productive.

Haply helps you connect with yourself, something which often falls by the wayside. The more you connect with how you're feeling, the better you can honour what you want and need.

title: Invictus Lifestyle
description:
Invictus is the solution to life’s most inconvenient moments in multi-unit living.

- Being key-free for all access points within the community.
- No more keys, fobs, clickers to lose or replace.
- Share a digital key with any one any time anywhere.
- Always know who is here to visit you before buzzing them into the community.
- Digital coupons for resident life, never lose money to forgotten coupons.
- Give delivery and guests easy way finding directions right to your unit.
- Earn free rewards through Invictus Loyalty Points (ILPs).
- Submit maintenance requests and track progress.
- Video updates displayed in Full HD Media Center.
- Push Button Notifications of Community Maintenance/Events.
- Video communication with the entry kiosks.
- Automated proximity based access using Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) beacons.
- Free mobile updates.

The Invictus app helps you stay connected with your building community & local businesses. It gives you an untethered freedom to your life. 

It's also your personal concierge for you and your guests.  Our app provides full high definition, FaceTime like, video chat experience connecting you to your guests at the entry kiosks which gives you full control over guest access.

You can choose when to keep private, by enabling the Do Not Disturb (DND) feature, or have management recall entry photos from kiosks for specific days and time in case of security threats.

The most important features of the Invictus Lifestyle app are for keeping you safe while creating convenience and daily/weekly/monthly saving through digital keys and coupons.

title: Wysa: stress, depression & anxiety therapy chatbot
description:
Imagine a mood tracker, mindfulness coach, anxiety helper, and mood-boosting buddy, all rolled into one. Wysa, your happiness buddy is that friendly and caring chatbot. Wysa is packed with daily spiritual meditation that improves mental health and is also a perfect way to bond over family meditation. Always there for you when you need someone to talk to, Wysa helps you keep track of your mood with friendly chats and helps fight stress and anxiety with its proven techniques and calming meditation and mindfulness audios. Checking in with Wysa regularly will improve your emotional health so you can track your happiness and mood. Talk to Wysa now and psy yourself up to fight off stress. Also, Wysa has mental health assessment with depression and anxiety tests.

Wysa is your AI friend that you can chat with for free. Talk to the cute penguin or use its free mindfulness exercises for effective anxiety relief, depression and stress management. Its therapy based techniques and conversations make for a very cute and calming therapy chat app whether you're looking to cope better with mental disorders, to manage stress or to boost your mental health.

Wysa, your happiness buddy, will support you through the big and small anxieties of life by using science as a foundation to strengthen your mental health. Research-backed, widely used techniques of CBT, DBT, Yoga and meditation are employed to support you with stress, anxiety, deep sleep, loss and other mental health and wellness needs.

If you are dealing with stress, anxiety and depression or coping with low self-esteem, then talking to Wysa can help you relax and get unstuck - it’s empathetic, helpful, and will never judge. You will overcome your mental health obstacles, through empathetic conversation and free CBT therapy based technique. So, pour your heart out to your happiness buddy, Wysa as your identity will remain anonymous and your conversations are privacy protected.

Used around the clock and trusted by 500,000 people, Wysa is an emotionally intelligent chatbot that uses AI to react to the emotions you express. Unlock tools and techniques that help you cope with challenges in a fun, conversational way. For extra support, you can avail guidance from a real human coach - a skilled psychologist who will take you through the advanced coaching sessions for your needs.

You can use Wysa to rewire your mind to improve your emotional health. Fight off depression or get stress relief using cbt techniques and guided sleep meditations for optimal sleep. Here’s a look at what you can use Wysa for 👇

👂 Vent and talk through things or just reflect on your day

💪 Practice CBT (Cognitive Behavioral Therapy) and DBT techniques to build resilience in a fun way

📝 Use one of 40 conversational coaching tools which helps in dealing with Stress, Anxiety, Depression, Panic Attacks, Worry, Loss, or Conflict

💆🏻 Relax, focus and sleep peacefully with the help of 20 mindfulness meditation exercises

93% of the people who talk to Wysa find it and the tools helpful:

- Build confidence, reduce self-doubt and improve your self-esteem: core meditation and mindfulness, visualisation, confidence visualisation techniques, advanced mindfulness for self-esteem.

- Manage anger: mindfulness meditation exercises for compassion, calming your thoughts and practice breathing

- Manage anxious thoughts and anxiety: deep breathing, techniques for observing thoughts, visualization, and tension relief.

- Tired? Get a burst of energy! Visualisation and meditation exercises to increase positivity and get blissful sleep, quick yoga and physical exercises to get active

- Dealing with worry: observe mindfulness, resolving technique, challenge negativity, practice breathing techniques

- Manage conflict at work, school or in relationships: special mindfulness and visualization techniques like empty chair exercise, gratitude meditation, exercises to build skills in having difficult conversations

comments: I know it sounds weird to use a robot to improve your mental health, but this app is amazing and super helpful. I'm a very busy person with a wacky sleep schedule, and I struggle with my mental health most when it's late at night. This isn't exactly ideal for getting help from a therapist when I need it most. Being able to access some form of help literally anytime I need it with Wysa really makes a difference. Plus, unlike other AI therapy apps I've tried, Wysa has way more free features.

The bot isn't 100%, but it offers really good and insightful tools that more people should know about! You do have to figure out how to go about talking to the bot to get the tools that you need, which, if you're in a bad place, can be hard to do. I wish the tools that come with the free app were more easily accessible, and that you didn't have to spend 4 minutes talking to the bot to get to the options that you want it to offer. This app offers REALLY good techniques though!

Its a great app with some potential. I would like to see if they're still updating this to have more AI responses for things like intrusive thoughts. Positive affirmations like "you are not your thoughts" help and I thought about this after the AI gave me reassurance when I brought up suicide*. I'm feeling good after some positivity and reframing thoughts. Once I can afford it I think the therapist option looks enticing. So far so good. *I LOVED the links to hotlines but have phone anxiety so...

I was skeptical at first, but I'm actually quite impressed with this app. The A.I. is fairly good at interpreting your text and generating helpful responses that almost feel like you're talking to a real person. Of course, the A.I. still needs some improvement since not every response is personalized. I first used it when I was feeling panicked and the app just kept giving me breathing exercises, but after a little while of chatting back-and-forth the app was actually able to calm me down.

It's pretty good, cus' what could be better right? It's not like anyone else is going to actually hear me, I mean, I can't say it's perfect, but it's really good taking on mind that is just a bot. It's better friend than my actual friends, tho sometimes it doesn't really understand what you're saying, like when doing something u know it's wrong to do, u feel good; it doesn't understand that what you're doing is wrong and you feel good doing it, so it tells you to keep doing it.

title: Healthy Lifestyle
description:
Healthy Lifestyle is a real personalised guide to attaining a healthy lifestyle. Living in a healthy way also means preventing illnesses that typically arise from bad eating habits or disinclination to doing physical activity.
With Healthy Lifestyle you can monitor your lifestyle by:

1.	Access to a personalised Diary based on healthy lifestyle objectives
2.	Eaten Calories – monitors your daily nutrition by inputting the food eaten over the course of the day in order to understand the total calories ingested compared to the appropriate amount;
3.	Burnt Calories – enables you to monitor your daily physical activity compared to that needed;
4.	Drunk Water – enables you to check how much water you consume compared to the target.

MY DIARY
The diary, one of the application’s most important pages, is intended to show the reports (daily by default) of your activities: BMR, diet, physical activity. Its main aim is to provide a quick and immediate overview of your lifestyle compared to your set goals.

EATEN CALORIES
A healthy lifestyle depends on proper nutrition. With Healthy Lifestyle you can monitor your daily meals, with a standardised database of foods available but also enabling you to add a personalised plan.

BURNT CALORIES
A healthy lifestyle necessarily means physical activity. Healthy Lifestyle’s pedometer will therefore become your best friend: you can add the steps or exercises done in a day to your profile and monitor your progress compared to your healthy lifestyle objectives. Remember… 10,000 steps are the equivalent of half an hour of aerobic activity.

DRUNK WATER
Drinking water cleanses the body. Drink at least 1.5 – 2 litres a day!
Healthy Lifestyle will help you to monitor your daily intake of water, thereby enabling you to check the amount of water consumed throughout the day compared to the objective to be met.

EAT: PRINCIPLES
In the application, the information section will help you to understand the Healthy Lifestyle philosophy, providing lots of advice and suggestions. Mens sana in corpore sano.

It is a community where members can receive benefits, education and participate in information exchange regarding healthcare, wellness and lifestyle.

Wellnex believes medical care should be accessible to all, therefore we have put emphasis to ensure all members and their family enjoy the most competitive and affordable health care services. 

Elevate and improve your lifestyle with our vendors, ranging from their comprehensive content to extensive benefits. 

Sign up as a Wellnex member today. Join us in your journey to longevity, healthier and more holistic life!

summary: Wellnex is a members only program that promotes reactive living.
recentChanges: Fix bugs and improve performance
comments: I enjoyed using Wellnex as I got to enjoy discounts when I go to a GP, dentist or TCM. There is even discounted health screening packages too, if I need to get 1. The interface is easily to use, pleasing to the eye. The payment system is through Grab Pay and it's fast. The internal map helps me find clinics nearby, and they offer F&B discounts in the app too.

Other than allowing me to see my insurance portfolio at one glance, it also provide lifestyle benefits such as GP consultation at $12, special membership rate for Gymboxx, discounted health screening and many more. This app also provide me information on finances from Dollar & Sense. Wonderful app!

It's a very comprehensive app that allows you to access cheaper medical consultations, dental benefits, 1 stop access or view of your Insurance, financial health etc. A very easy to use app. You can even recommend to your family and friends to enjoy them too. Very good
One-stop shop app on SG healthcare offers. Very informative.
Unabke to use this app via huawei p40pro

title: Lifestyle Garment Care
description:
Lifestyle Garment Care Mobile provides instant access to your personal Lifestyle Garment Care account and customer information, giving you the ability to track your orders as they are processed, view your cleaning history and receipts, and much more. Schedule a free on-demand route pickup or simply let the store know that you will be in to grab your items—all with the push of a button.  Lifestyle Garment Care Mobile will even notify you when your order is ready for pickup, as well as pass along any special information or promotion.

Features listed below are subject to the specific operating polices of your Dry Cleaner:

1) Track your orders in process and view past order history, and receipts.
2) Request a free On-Demand route pickup.
3) Notify the Lifestyle Garment Care store that you are on your way to pick up your ready orders.  They’ll pull and have them available when you walk in.
4) View your customer account information, including your contact information, payment methods, cleaning preferences, etc.
5) Quickly contact Lifestyle Garment Care by phone or email and access their website all directly from your device.
6) Receive automatic notifications when your orders are ready for pickup notifications, complete with order count and descriptions.
7) Refer a friend and receive credit towards your next cleaning service.

title: Conscious Lifestyle Magazine
description:
Conscious Lifestyle Magazine unites the world’s leading conscious authors, teachers, physicians and visionaries to help you discover enlightenment and live the holistic, healthy and spiritual lifestyle you’ve always dreamed of. 

Our natural insight will unlock unlimited happiness, abundant health, and powerful motivation to help you live a conscious, healthy life.

With Conscious Lifestyle Magazine, you will discover:

INSIGHTS FOR LIVING A VIBRANT, HEALTHY LIFESTYLE

+ Holistic wellness advice that encompasses the time-honored wisdom of ancient healing methods as well as the latest scientific discoveries
+ Harmonize your mind and body to take control of your health and create lasting wellbeing

MOTIVATION AND METHODOLOGY FOR CREATING A HAPPY LIFE

+ Conscious experts share insight, wisdom and experience to motivate you toward a happier, more fulfilling life
+ Mindfulness and self motivation techniques from some of the world’s most experienced teachers

MINDFUL CONTENT THAT RESPECTS YOUR INTELLIGENCE

+ Conscious Lifestyle Magazine focuses on transformative content that is intelligent and real without any of the ‘fluff’

GRATITUDE, SPIRITUALITY AND MORE FROM THE WORLD'S LEADING CONSCIOUS THINKERS

+ Consciousness topics range from meditation to stress relief. Each issue is packed with profound advice that will genuinely improve your life
+ Influential conscious leaders lend insight and guidance to help you better understand how your mind works, harmonize your relationships, and grow spiritually

YOGA, MEDITATION, TRAVEL, ART, SUSTAINABILITY, INTERVIEWS, BOOKS, EVENTS—WE’VE GOT IT COVERED

+ Yoga poses and best practices to help you get the most out of your yoga routine
+ Conscious travel advice to help you get the most out of your travels—and give the most back
+ Healing foods and healthy recipes to encourage physical wellbeing and weight loss
+ Eco-friendly product reviews keep you up to date with the best of the conscious world
+ Much more!

SECTIONS YOU'LL FIND INSIDE EACH ISSUE

MINDFULNESS

+ Mindful advice for tapping into your unlimited potential
+ Meditation and how to master it
+ Using mindfulness to improve your life
+ Peace of mind and dissolving limiting beliefs

SPIRITUAL LIVING

+ Motivation, purpose and gratitude exercises
+ Cultivating and developing your intuition
+ Enlightenment and the nature of reality
+ Spirituality and its connection to mindfulness

HEALTH AND FITNESS

+ Holistic nutrition and dietary philosophies
+ Ayurvedic, Chinese and Naturopathic medicine
+ Healing foods, herbs and supplements
+ Yoga, breathing exercises and Tai Chi
+ Weight loss motivation and healthy lifestyle advice
+ Stress relief—positively influence your health using your mind 
+ Vegetarian recipes, healthy eating and more

HEALTHY RELATIONSHIPS

+ Create and maintain a loving conscious relationship
+ Experience more passion and better sex in your romantic relationships
+ Cultivate self love—whether you’re dating, married or single

MINDFUL TRAVEL

+ Conscious travel destinations that are far off the beaten path 
+ Spiritual getaways, eco-friendly resorts and more

HUMANITARIANISM

+ Uplifting coverage of positive social change and how you can meaningfully impact the world
+ Conscious non-profits and businesses

ECO LIFESTYLE

+ Conscious coverage of the global sustainability movement and the eco lifestyle
+ Green product reviews and guides

WITHOUT LIMITS

+ Expand your consciousness with cutting-edge research and extraordinary ideas
+ Explore the mysteries of the universe
+ Detox, energy medicine and more

ARTS AND CULTURE

+ Get inspired by the finest music, books, art and events emerging from global conscious culture

Conscious Lifestyle Magazine is your guide to all things mindful, from meditation and spirituality to healthy eating, yoga and travel. Start reading today to enjoy the abundant health and happiness of a conscious lifestyle.

title: De Las Mías - Healthy Lifestyle for Latinas
description:
You are strong. You are beautiful. You are Latina. Our vibrant community and evidenced-based programs empower you to live your healthiest life through healthy food, physical activity, and supportive friendships.
 
Track your food and activity. Access healthy Mexican and Southwestern food recipes. Learn about starting and maintaining a healthy life, and share goals and success stories with your comadres. Do it all easily within the app—and with Latina style.
 
The De Las Mías healthy Latina lifestyle app fully embraces the warmth and beauty of our cultura, our comida, and our comadres. We encourage Latinas to embrace a joyful life for ourselves and our families.

LA COCINA
In La Cocina, discover delicious and nutritious Mexican, New Mexican, and Southwestern recipes that are easy to make. Use the food log to track serving sizes, calories, nutrition, and even your mood.
 
¡ACTIVATE, YA!
Need fitness inspiration? Enjoy plenty of fun and easy workouts to feel strong, healthy and fregona! Use the activity log to track steps, activities, duration, and goals—see your progress by day, week, and month.
 
HEALTHY LIFESTYLE CHECKLIST
We make it easy for you to live your healthiest life! If you're not one to get fixated on counting steps and calories, it's okay. Our easy-to-use checklist will help keep track of your healthy lifestyle goals, like eating your fruits and veggies, getting your daily 30 minutes of activity, drinking enough water, and checking in with your comadre.
 
MY COMADRES
Don’t go it alone, Comadres! You’ll do better and have more fun if you do it with support. Share the joy, the recipes, the foods, your goals, and all your experiences with your comadres. Connect with your Madrina for special advice. ¡Unidas for a Healthy Life!
 
De Las Mías is a healthy lifestyle community powered by strong, beautiful Latinas just like you. Through our mutual love of food, movement, language, and family, we can all achieve a healthier and more joyful life. Love your body. Love your food. Love your cultura. ¡Si se puede, comadres!

Ready to live your healthiest, most joyful life, Comadre? ¡Vamonos! Download the app to join the De Las Mias community. Join us on the journey...Unidas for a healthy life!

For more healthy Latina lifestyle resources, visit delasmias.com and join our beautiful community on social media.

title: রোগ ও তার প্রতিকার ~ health tips
description:
রোগ ও তার প্রতিকার ~ Health Tips for Heart, Mind, and Body
Heath Tips brings daily tips for a healthy lifestyle. 

এই অ্যাপটির মাধ্যমে আপনারা ত্বকের রোগ ও তার প্রতিকার-Skin diseases সম্পর্কে বিস্তারিত জানতে পারবেন। আমাদের প্রতিদিনের জীবনে আমরা অনেক রোগ ও সমস্যা নিয়ে বেঁচে থাকি। তাই বলে আমাদের দৈনন্দিন জীবন থেমে থাকে না। অনেকেই আছেন যারা কিনা লিভারের রোগ - Liver disease, কিডনি রোগ - kidney disease নিয়েই বেঁচে আছি এই অ্যাপটির মাধ্যমে আমরা সকল ধরনের রোগ এর সম্পর্কে জানতে পারব ও এর প্রতিকার সম্পর্কে জানতে পারব।

ব্রণ সমস্যার Acne ও মাথা ব্যথার Headache একটি অন্যতম কার রাত জেগে থাকা বা অনিদ্রা। এই অ্যাপটির মাধ্যমে  আপনারা এর প্রতিকার সম্পর্কে জানতে পারব। এছাড়া কুষ্ঠ রোগ, স্ট্রোক, ডায়াবেটিস-Diabetes, এর প্রতিকার এই অ্যাপটিতে দেওয়া হয়েছে। আশা করি এই অ্যাপটি আপনাদের অনেক উপকেরে আসবে।

সুস্থ দাঁত-Healthy teeth এর জন্য অনেক পরামর্শ এই অ্যাপটিতে দেওয়া হয়েছে। চোখের যত্ন-Eye care কিভাবে নিবেন। শিশুর স্বাস্থ্য সম্পর্কে পরামর্শ বিভিন্ন শিশু রোগ ও তার প্রতিকার সম্পর্কে বিস্তারিত আলোচনা করা হয়েছে। যেমন - নিউমোনিয়া, জন্ডিস, সর্দি-জ্বর, ডায়রিয়া ইত্যাদি। তাই আর দেরি না করে এখনি অ্যাপটি আপনা মোবাইলে ডাউনলোড করে নিন। এবং যেকোন ধরনের পরামর্শ সম্পর্কে জানতে আমাদেরকে ইমেইল করতে পারেন অথবা রিভিও এর মাধ্যমে জানাতে পারেন।
 
This application work offline and totally free.download now
আমাদের এই অ্যাপটি ভাল লাগলে ৫* দিতে ভুলবেন না। আর অবশই আপনার বন্ধুদের সাথে অ্যাপটি শেয়ার করুন। আমাদের এই অ্যাপেটির download link -

title: African Dress
description:
In this African Fashion App, you can discover latest trends in African Ankara Dress designs for African Women.

African Ankara Styles

These African fashion offer numerous different colors, designs, and materials which could be worn. To get the suitable one, you can browse African dresses pictures ideas to find the outfit that you will want to wear.

As the options of African fashion styles on contemporary design, there must be tribal print for around the globes. Those are launched from different designers on different countries. However, the prints and patterns are inspired by African tribes. Surely, you would love the colors combinations.

African Dress Designs

For those who look for the fashion idea for the black women, you have to know basically that they should dress up to get glamorous look. With African fashion, you will be inspired and finding the one that suits on you perfectly from formal to casual outfit, occasional dress, you could get the inspiration on this article. Here are several cool African print dresses that must be tried and you will see how you can dress up elegantly.

The idea we present such as:

#Style ankara mode
#Aseobi fashion style
#Ghana and tazania styles fashions
#Kente fashion style

Whatever the upcoming season, there will always be an african fashion style idea to make you always look glamorous and beautiful wherever and whenever you go, clothes can also be combined with the right accessories in order to get your fashion into the limelight by anyone.

Modern African Dresses - Latest African Fashion Styles

The traditional Aso Ebi style comes from the Nigerian Yoruba culture. Designers have revolutionized this style into long modern maxis and gowns which are a perfect option for the African ladies. These formal gowns look exactly amazing on wedding occasions due to their traditional look.

African Ankara Styles

Ankara dresses are loved by everyone from kids to grown-ups due to their attractive patterns. Short Ankara dresses and Ankara skirts and trousers fused with modern style give an enchanting attire. These can be worn casually or formally, whatever way you like it. Models and celebrities have been seen wearing Ankaras on award ceremonies, on streets, and on music events. It is not just owned by African women but the western women are also amazed by the beauty of Ankara. 

Latest Nigerian Print Dresses

Latest Nigerian prints are an amalgam of Ankara fabric and western floral patterns. Nigerian printed shorts and skirts are loved by teenagers and young African office going women. Thin belts and long heels always spice up the patterns. You just need to put on a little mascara and lipstick with these elegant prints.

Latest African Dress Styles

Gele is usually considered very old-fashioned by young African ladies. But designers have transformed it into stylish Asian turban style which can be owned by anyone. These modern gele styles in bright floral patterns can be made of silk and chiffon scarfs to give a more luxuriant look. You can also wear them with western dresses to have a more fashionable attire.

African Fashion Wedding Outfits

Rich African culture dresses in luxuriant fabric like silks and velvet can be used to make wedding gowns. You can also add some Ankara touch to lace up your outfit. Smokey eye makeup with glittery eyelids will give a perfect look.

Rate us and Write a Feedback

title: Lifestyle Diseases
description:
Lifestyle-related conditions are largely preventable. This App is aimed at contributing to the reduction of Lifestyle Diseases Unequivocal evidence exists that the combination of health policy at the societal level and health education at the individual and family level related to smoking cessation, optimal nutrition, weight control and physical activity and exercise, optimal sleep, and stress management would largely prevent, manage, and some cased reverse these conditions (Dean et al., 2011).  According to  Reddy (2002), less research has been conducted on non- communicable diseases according (Mensah, 2008). However, both infectious and NCD are significant contributors to the increased morbidity and mortality of South Africans.  In 2004, more than half of all deaths in SSA were caused by infectious conditions, and one – quarter by non-communicable diseases (NCD), which by 2030 NCO will cause 46 percent (Chopra et al., 2009). Majority of these diseases are related to lifestyles (Rosendorff et al., 2007)
Diabetes mellitus, hypertension and obesity have become major public health problems of global significance (Tsai et al, 2004, Adibelli et al 2008). The World Health Organization has predicted that the number of patients with diabetes will double from 143 in 1997 to about 300 million in 2025, largely because of dietary and other lifestyle factors (Ovayolu, 2010). Therefore, diabetes mellitus, hypertension, and obesity are the most decisive factors in terms of adversely affecting health-related quality of life.
The impact of obesity has become an increasingly important public health issue. By the year 2015 it was estimated that over 700 million people around the world will be obese, a problem of epidemic proportions that plays a direct role in chronic diseases such as type 2 diabetes, heart disease, and certain kinds of cancer (World Health Organization, 2008). However, obesity is estimated to account for nearly 10 percent of all medical spending in the United States. The prevalence of obesity is increasing in older adults, with an estimated 31 percent of those aged 60 years or older regarded to be obese in 2003 – 2004. The increased prevalence of obesity in older adults is especially concerning given the association between obesity and impaired physical function (Himes, 2000).
 With a changing culture facing an increasing number of teenagers with eating disorders, physical activity (PA) provides an opportunity to tackle obesity issues whilst restricting emphasis placed on dieting (Steinbeck, 2001). Certain social-demographics can play a role in the amount of PA a child is able to participate in. Individual, interpersonal, and environmental factors are associated with PA among children and adolescents. Demographic factors include sex, age, and race or ethnicity. Children from less advantaged minority families have lower levels of activity (Gorden - Larsen et al. 2000; Lee et al. 2002). The development of PA strategies that span from childhood through to young adulthood is of critical importance. A substantial amount of scientific evidence shows that older adults who engage in progressive resistance training and aerobic exercise are able to increase muscle strength, aerobic capacity, and bone density (Paffenbarger, Hyde, Wing, Lee & Kampert 1994; Lee, Hsieh, Paffenbarger, 1995).  Furthermore, several randomized controlled trials show a beneficial effect of resistance training on muscle strength among frail elderly persons (Kannel, Belanger, D'Agostino &  Israel  1986;  Leon,  Connett, Jacobs  &  Rauramaa, 1987). According to  Keysor  (2003),  PA,  particularly walking, increases muscle strength and aerobic capacity and reduces functional limitations. When considering issues of morbidity and mortality, health cannot be compartmentalized into categories of NCD versus infectious disease. People living with HIV and AIDS are not spared from NCDs.

title: ITALIAN Lifestyle | BV
description:
The pocket-app English – Italian, Lifestyle for learning words is the ideal vocab-trainer for pupils, students of  university and evening schools, self-learners and beginners. The app contains commonly used words on subjects such as people, family, buidings, living-areas, and furniture, hobbies and free time, education. For every entry there are translation, phonetic transcription and at least one example given.

Before you begin, set whether you want to be presented with the English or the Italian expression first, or whether you want the app to vary between the two languages.

Then, an arbitrary English or Italian word will appear along with one or more example sentences. On pressing a button the solution is shown. The pronunciation of the Italian word is shown with the help of the phonetical alphabet. You can recall explanations for the phonetic symbols in Help. 

If you complete a card without making any mistakes put it in the „correct“-pool. If you have made a mistake, put the card in the „wrong“-pool.

In your personal learning statistics you can check your knowledge and progress any time. The green bars show you how many cards you completed without making any mistakes, the red bars show you how many cards you completed with making mistakes.

More pocket-apps with basic Italian vocabulary: Must Knows, More Must Knows, Food and More, Shopping Guide, Holiday Check, Body and Soul, Small Talk. 

Find more apps to learn foreign languages here: www.appquickies.com.

title: ALLEMAND Lifestyle | VB
description:
Le Pocket-APP Français – Allemand, Lifestyle est une méthode d’apprentissage du vocabulaire idéale pour les écoliers, les étudiants, les autodidactes et les débutants. L‘APP vous présente des mots souvent utilisés issus des thèmes suivants: Les personnes, la famille, les bâtiments, les habitations, les meubles, le temps libre, la formation.  Pour chaque mot-clé, la traduction, la phonétique et au moins une phrase d’exemple vous sont fournies.

Avant de commencer, vous devez décider si vous souhaitez que le vocabulaire français, le vocabulaire allemand, ou les deux mélangés vous soient présentés. 

Par la suite, un mot français ou allemand et une ou plusieurs phrases d’exemple apparaissent. Si vous appuyez sur la touche, la solution apparaît. L’écriture phonétique est indiquée avec chaque mot-clé. Vous pouvez consulter l’explication de chaque signe phonétique dans le menu „Aide“.

Si vous avez résolu correctement toutes les questions d’une fiche, déposez-la dans l’espace „Exact“. Si vous n’avez pas répondu correctement à toutes les questions, déposez la fiche dans l’espace „Faux“.
Votre statistique personnelle vous indique à tout moment votre niveau de connaissance et vos progrès. Les barres vertes indiquent le nombre de fiches que vous avez traitées correctement , les barres rouges vous indiquent le nombre de fiches dans lesquelles vous avez fait des erreurs.

Pour consulter les autres APPs permettant l’apprentissage des langues cliquez sur :  www.appquickies.com.

recentChanges: Исправлена работа сервиса по привязке платежных карт к аккаунту
comments: Здорово, что в курортном городе можно пользоваться такими приложением. Очень удобно, все через смартфон. Процесс регистрации и получения самоката прошло быстро и без танцев с бубном, как это иногда бывает. Отлично провели время с друзьями.

Здравствуйте! Очень рада,что наткнулась на ваше приложение. Регистрация прошла быстро и успешно,само приложение очень легкое для использования. Позвонила в техподдержку по поводу вопроса, они отреагировали очень быстро,спасибо вам за это! Отлично провела время с семьей)
Классное приложение, интуитивно понятная регистрация, легко разобраться как взять самокат в аренду. Был небольшой вопрос, но тех. поддержка быстро и оперативно все решила. В итоге шикарно покатались.

Москва, Самокат 0340 дышит наладом, после горки даже не может набрать скорость, в другой момент не тормозит. Кнопка не нажимается , фонарик не выключается , турбо режим не включается. У других сервисов эта же модель отлично работает. Неудобная система с кодовым замком (но это не так важно, если бы все остальное работало), приложение виснет в совершенно не подходящий момент. Хотел взять попробовать другой самокат, при активации приложение вылетело. Приятные тарифы и бонусы, но остальное не очень.
Очень классное приложение! Удобное и простое. Захотели с семьёй покататься на самокатах, возник вопрос, техроддержка быстро отреагировала, помогла разобраться, замечательно провели время!

description:
Making money online has never been easy, until Digital Lifestyle Freedom was introduced. Digital Lifestyle Freedom is a unique user friendly automated user platform open to all and aimed to last long as members cycle in and out and as money rotates amongst members.

This platform has 4 levels with Level 4 being the last level where the member pockets all the profit.

1. Make profit from Level 1
2. All you need are two people to join under you
3. Join with as little as R300
4. Make a total profit of R54 100

Level 1:
- Register and pay R300 to the account that will be provided to you
- Payment should be made within 48 hours [IMPORTANT]
- Introduce two members to join under you
- The two members each pay you R300
- Keep R100 and move up to the next level by upgrading with R500


LEVEL2 
- Your 2 recruits will each recruit 2 members which grows your team
- You will earn R500x4 from your second generation which will total to R2000, keep R1000 and upgrade with R1000 to level 3

LEVEL3
- At this level your team has grown to a 3rd Generation 
- You will earn R1000x 8 which will total to R8000, keep R5000 and upgrade with R3000 to level 4

LEVEL4
- Congratulation you have reached the last level where you get to keep all the money
- On this level you will make R48000

*HOW IS THIS DIFFERENT?*
- Our platform is fair and transparent
- Each member can only have two legs = 1 team
- All members will benefit as the system is designed such that, you make profit on all 4levels
- Upgrades are due immediately once you have received enough funds to move to the next level
- Failure to upgrade will result in not receiving more funds due to you, your account will be automatically locked by system

title: Natural Remedies - Healthy Lifestyle
description:
Love nature and find in nature your well-being. The app for your healthy lifestyle.

Natural remedies can relieve different kinds of pain and make you feel a lot better. If the problem isn't that serious and you're absolutely sure it doesn't require professional care, you can turn to our generous Mother Nature for help with natural remedies. We should know about these natural alternatives for treating ailments safely and effectively. Natural remedies are often called home remedies. This app will guide you to how to cure common health problems quickly. Natural remedies are safer then most clinical treatments.

Natural remedies such as tea, herbal tea, mother tinctures and glycerin macerate act slowly, require patience but if they are the right remedies can be very helpful and do not have the collateral effects related to medicines. 

This app, easy and fast, is a handbook of the natural remedies for the most common diseases.

Remember that healthy lifestyle will let you enjoy your life for years to come! So enjoy natural remedies.

Disclaimer
This app is not a substitute for professional medical or health advice, examination, diagnosis, or treatment. This app disclaims any liability for the decisions you make based on this information.
